;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: #000000;">S40 1UA</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;"><strong><em><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;"><span style="font-size: small; color: #000000;">We are an equal opportunities employer</span></span></em></strong><strong><em></em></strong></p>', '2014-11-05', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '2014-10-22 09:23:43', '2014-10-22 09:25:51', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, ''),
(16, 'TALENTED CRIMINAL SOLICITOR', 'We are seeking an experienced advocate used to working in the Magistrates Courts with at least 3 to 5 years PQE, must be duty qualified.', '<p><strong>12 month contract to cover maternity leave.</strong></p>\r\n<p>This &lsquo;hands on&rsquo; role involves dealing with a full caseload of both publically funded and private work, out of hours police station rota and assisting in the day to day management of an established and progressive department.</p>\r\n<p>Salary negotiable.</p>\r\n<p>Please email/post all CVs detailing experience and current salary to:</p>\r\n<p><a href="mailto:lsg@bannerjones.co.uk">lsg@bannerjones.co.uk</a></p>\r\n<p>24 Glumangate<br />Chesterfield<br />Derbyshire<br />S40 1UA.</p>\r\n<p><em>We are an equal opportunities employer</em></p>\r\n<p><a href="../personal/vacancies" target="_blank"></a></p>', '2015-02-13', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '2015-01-29 10:09:16', '2015-01-29 10:18:14', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, ''),
(17, 'Private Client Secretary', 'We are seeking a Private Client Secretary to join our secretarial team based in Chesterfield.', '<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Full Time hours</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Hours of business are Monday to Friday 9.00 am to 5.00 pm</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Salary is negotiable dependant upon experience</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The successful candidate should be highly organised, accurate and committed to meeting deadlines whilst remaining calm under pressure.&nbsp; Good interpersonal skills and proficiency in providing secretarial services including audio/copy typing, diary management, production of accurate letters/documents utilising Case Management/IT systems whilst ensuring the highest levels of speed, accuracy, presentation and confidentiality.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You will be expected to carry out a wide range of duties requiring confident client liaison by responding quickly and efficiently to all telephone calls, ensuring that an appropriate answer is given, or that an accurate message is taken and then passed to the relevant member of the team for actioning.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>It will be necessary for you to provide an efficient and professional service for new and existing clients over the telephone and face to face, to promote the Company&rsquo;s image and increase business.&nbsp; You should have strong document production, matter management, billing, record keeping and administrative skills, with the ability to prioritise your work whilst also working as part of a team and by your own initiative.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Previous experience is preferable but not essential as training will be provided.</p>\r\n<p>We are an energetic, forward thinking and award winning law firm with  offices in Sheffield, Chesterfield, Dronfield, Ilkeston, Derby,  Nottingham, Mansfield, and Bulwell offering an exceptional quality  service to our clients.</p>\r\n<p>From the 1<sup>st</sup>&nbsp;September 2013 Bilton Hammond became part of the Banner Jones Group and still trade as Bilton Hammond in Mansfield.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Please email your Personal Statement attaching Curriculum Vitae, together with details of current salary to: </strong><strong><strong><a href="mailto:HumanResources@bannerjones.co.uk">HumanResources@bannerjones.co.uk</a></strong></strong><strong></strong><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Address:&nbsp;&nbsp;24 Glumangate, Chesterfield S40 1UA<br />Tel:&nbsp; 01246&nbsp;560560</strong><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Closing date is 3<sup>rd</sup> July 2015&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n<p><em>We are an equal opportunities employer</em></p>', '2015-07-03', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '2015-03-19 15:49:44', '2015-06-29 09:01:22', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, ''),
(18, 'Experienced Family Law Solicitor/FILEX required', 'Minimum of 3 to 5 years PQE or equivalent experience in Private Family Law. ', '<p><strong>BANNER JONES &amp; BILTON HAMMOND SOLICITORS </strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Experienced Family Solicitor/FILEX required<br /></strong><strong>Based in Mansfield&nbsp;<br /></strong><strong>Full Time hours<br /></strong><strong>Hours of business are Monday to Friday 9.00 am to 5.00 pm</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Salary is negotiable dependant upon experience</strong> &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We are seeking applications from experienced Family Solicitors/FILEX with a minimum of 3 to 5 years PQE or equivalent experience in Private Family Law.&nbsp; This exciting business development opportunity requires someone with drive and passion to join our Legal 500 recommended Family team.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The successful candidate will be experienced in all aspects of Private Family Law, will work as part of our team but the ability to build and manage your own case load independently is essential.&nbsp; You will also be required to represent clients at Court and have confidence in conducting your own Advocacy.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To be considered for this position you must have strong interpersonal and business development skills with the ability to work on your own initiative with minimal supervision, have a clear and professional telephone manner, possess excellent computer skills, be numerate, able to meet deadlines whilst remaining calm under pressure with the ability to keep meticulous records. The position would suit someone who is highly organised, accurate and who is committed to business development.&nbsp; Excellent all round communication skills and attention to detail is essential.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Own transport/valid UK driver licence holder is essential to this post.</p>\r\n<p>We are an energetic, forward thinking and award winning law firm with  offices in Sheffield, Chesterfield, Dronfield, Ilkeston, Derby,  Nottingham, Mansfield, and Bulwell offering an exceptional quality  service to our clients.&nbsp;</p>\r\nFrom the 1<sup>st</sup> September 2013 Bilton Hammond merged with Banner Jones Solicitors to become part of the Banner Jones Group. &nbsp; <br />\r\n<p><strong>Please email your Personal Statement attaching Curriculum Vitae, together with details of current salary to Lisa Gill, Human Resources Manager: </strong><strong><a href="mailto:HumanResources@bannerjones.co.uk">HumanResources@bannerjones.co.uk</a></strong><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Address:&nbsp;&nbsp;24 Glumangate, Chesterfield S40 1UA.&nbsp; Tel:&nbsp; 01246&nbsp;560560</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Closing date is 3<sup>rd</sup> July 2015 </strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><em>We are an equal opportunities employer</em></strong></p>', '2015-07-03', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '2015-05-29 11:52:02', '2015-06-29 09:01:19', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, ''),
(19, 'Administration Assistant ', 'Bilton Hammond Solicitors (part of the Banner Jones Group) are looking for an Administration Assistant based within our Mansfield office.', '<p><strong>BANNER JONES LTD &amp; BILTON HAMMOND SOLICITORS</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Administration Assistant required<br /></strong><strong>Based in Mansfield&nbsp;<br /></strong><strong>Full Time hours - permanent contract<br />Hours of business are Monday to Friday 9.00 am to 5.00 pm</strong><br /><strong>Immediate Start.</strong></p>\r\n<p>We are an energetic, forward thinking and award winning law firm with offices in Sheffield, Chesterfield, Dronfield, Ilkeston, Derby, Nottingham, Mansfield, and Bulwell offering an exceptional quality service to our clients.</p>\r\n<p>From the 1<sup>st</sup>&nbsp;September 2013 Bilton Hammond merged with Banner Jones Solicitors to become part of the Banner Jones Group.</p>\r\n<p>You will be expected to carry out a wide range of duties which will include collating of documentation, photocopying and scanning, faxing, filing and other administration tasks.</p>\r\n<p>You will also have good communication skills, the ability to prioritise your work whilst also working as part of a team and on own initiative.</p>\r\n<p>Please apply in writing with CVs and a supporting statement outlining your suitability and/or experience to:-</p>\r\n<p>Grant Hodgkiss <br /> Banner Jones Ltd <br /> 24 Glumangate <br /> Chesterfield <br /> S40 1UA</p>\r\n<p>Or alternatively by email to:-</p>\r\n<p><a href="mailto:gnh@bannerjones.co.uk">gnh@bannerjones.co.uk</a></p>\r\n<p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<a href="mailto:gnh@bannerjones.co.uk"></a><strong><em>We are an equal opportunities employer</em></strong></p>', '2015-09-16', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '2015-09-02 10:39:51', '2015-09-02 10:50:24', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '');
