(1, 'Glumangate', '24 Glumangate\r\nChesterfield\r\nDerbyshire ', 'S40 1UA', '01246 560560', '<h3>Google+</h3>\r\n<p>For more information, or to leave a review for this office, please visit our Google+ page <a href="http://plus.google.com/+bannerjones/posts" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>\r\n<h3>Services Offered</h3>\r\n<p>Residential Property, Wills &amp; Probate, Employment Law, Dispute Resolution, Business Legal Services, Commercial Property.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold;">Directions</span></p>\r\n<h3>From  Sheffield</h3>\r\n<p>Take the A61 (Dual carriageway) to Chesterfield. Stay on this  road  until you come to the large roundabout with Tesco&rsquo;s on your left hand   side.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Go straight across at this  roundabout and after 1 mile take the slip road A632 sign posted  Chesterfield/Matlock/Bolsover.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>At the  lights turn left, under the bridge to the roundabout and then turn right sign  posted Town Centre.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Follow the road up  the hill through two sets of lights past the Crooked Spire on the left, to the  lights.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Keep in the right hand lane but  go straight on leaving Eyres on your left hand side.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Up to the next lights and again go straight  on.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Stay on this road called Saltergate  for&nbsp; 250 yards (Co-Op on your left hand  side) and Glumangate is on your left hand side.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Turn left at the lights and our office is on  the right hand side.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you are driving  (as Glumangate is a one way street) take the  second turning on your left (after  Glumangate) on to Rose Hill.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>At the  bottom turn left onto Knifesmithgate and Glumangate is the second on the left  hand side.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Turn left and we are 50  yards up on the left hand side.</p>\r\n<p><em>There is limited parking outside the office  