(12, 'Guides', 'guides', 'Free Guides and Factsheets', 12, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Please click on the link to view the relevant guide.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Conveyancing &amp; Residential Property</span></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Buying Your House Guide'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/4_buying a home process one pages.pdf?1300809818" target="_blank">Buying a House</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Selling Your House Guide'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/5_selling a home process one page.pdf?1300809842" target="_blank">Selling a House</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Buying and Selling Guide'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/62_Residential Conveyancing - Buying and Selling Houses - Updated 07.04.14.pdf?1396883544" target="_blank">Buying and Selling</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Help to Buy Scheme'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/69_Residential Conveyancing - Help to buy scheme - How to buy a help to buy home.pdf?1400502458" target="_blank">Help to Buy Scheme</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Employment Law</span></p>\r\n<p>Guide to&nbsp;<a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Discrimination Fact Sheet'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/91_Employment Law - Discrimination Fact Sheet for Employers.pdf?1408705425" target="_blank">Discrimination for Employers</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Unfair Dismissal Guide'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/93_Employment Law - Unfair dismissal guide for employees.pdf?1408705469" target="_blank">Unfair Dismissal For Employees</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Redundancy Procedure Guide'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/92_Employment Law - Redundancy procedure guide.pdf?1408705445" target="_blank">Redundancy Procedure For Employers</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Disciplinary Action Guide'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/76_Employment Law - Disciplinary Action Guide for Employers.pdf?1403267786" target="_blank">Disciplinary Action For Employers</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Wills &amp; Probate</span></p>\r\n<p>Guide to&nbsp;<a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/13_Factsheet - Lasting Power of Attorney.docx?1322579386" target="_blank">Lasting Power of Attorney</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to&nbsp;<a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/6_What to do when someone dies FD version.pdf?1300810419" target="_blank">Losing a loved one</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to&nbsp;<a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/8_Retired and living feb 2011 dps.pdf?1300810934" target="_blank">Planning for your future</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/8_Retired and living feb 2011 dps.pdf?1300810934" target="_blank"></a>Guide to <a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/14_Factsheet - 10 Reasons why you need a Will.doc?1322580008" target="_blank">Writing a Will, 10 reasons why you need one</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Divorce</span></p>\r\n<p>Fact Sheet:&nbsp;<a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Family law A Guide To Divorce and Separation'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/66_Family Law - Divorce and Separation Fact Sheet.pdf?1400499976" target="_blank">Divorce and Separation</a></p>\r\n<p>Fact Sheet: <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Divorce Across the Years'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/118_DivorceInfographicV3.pdf?1424864905" target="_blank">Divorce Across the Years</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Funding Your Divorce'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/80_Family Law - Funding Your Divorce.pdf?1403267833" target="_blank">Funding Your Divorce</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Grounds For Divorce'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/85_Family Law - Grounds for divorce explained.pdf?1408702622" target="_blank">Grounds For Divorce</a></p>\r\n<p>Fact Sheet:&nbsp;<a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Complex divorce fact sheet'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/102_Complex Divorce.pdf?1414500829" target="_blank">Complex Divorce</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/153_BANKRUPTCY AND DIVORCE OR CIVIL PARTNERSHIP DISSOLUTION GUIDE - Bilton Hammond.docx?1437564966" target="_blank">Bankruptcy and Divorce/Civil Partnership Dissolution</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/152_CIVIL PARTNERSHIP DISSOLUTION - Bilton Hammond.docx?1437564961" target="_blank">Civil Partnership Dissolution</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/151_DIVORCE GUIDE - Bilton Hammond.docx?1437564955" target="_blank">Divorce</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/150_FINANCIAL MATTERS - Bilton Hammond.docx?1437564948" target="_blank">Financial Matters</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/149_FINANCIAL MATTERS FOR COHABITANTS ON SEPARATION - Bilton Hammond.docx?1437564942" target="_blank">Financial Matters for Cohabitants on Separation</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/148_PENSION IN DIVORCE - Bilton Hammond.docx?1437564925" target="_blank">Pension in Divorce</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Family</span></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Family law What Counts as Domestic Violence'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/65_Family Law - Legal Aid - What counts as domestic violence.pdf?1400498116" target="_blank">What Counts as Domestic Violence</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Family law Evidence that Children are at Risk'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/64_Family Law - Legal Aid - What counts as evidence that children are at risk.pdf?1400498096" target="_blank">Providing Evidence that Children are at Risk</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Care</span></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/144_CARE PROCEEDINGS - Bilton Hammond.docx?1437564708" target="_blank">Care Proceedings</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/145_GUIDE TO CHILDRENS MATTERS - Bilton Hammond.docx?1437564715" target="_blank">Children Matters</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/146_GUIDE TO INJUNCTIONS - Bilton Hammond.docx?1437564721" target="_blank">Injunctions</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/147_PARENTAL RESPONSIBILITIES GUIDE - Bilton Hammond.docx?1437564727" target="_blank">Parental Responsibilities</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Driving &amp; Traffic Offences</span></p>\r\n<p>Fact Sheet: <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Careless Driving Guide'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/94_Driving Offences - Careless Driving Guide.pdf?1409044884" target="_blank">Dangerous, Careless and Reckless Driving</a></p>\r\n<p>Fact Sheet: <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Speeding in Sheffield'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/115_Speeding.pdf?1420627418" target="_blank">Speeding in Sheffield</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Mobile Phone Offences Guide'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/96_Driving Offences - Mobile phone driving guide.pdf?1409044951" target="_blank">Mobile Phone Driving Offences</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Drink Driving Offences Guide'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/95_Driving Offences - Drink Driving Penalty Guide.pdf?1409044931" target="_blank">Drink Driving Offences</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Totting up Guide'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/100_Driving Offences - Totting up guide.pdf?1409045004" target="_blank">Totting Up</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Speeding Offences Guide'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/101_Driving Offences - Speeding Offences Infographic.pdf?1409053156" target="_blank">Speeding Offences</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Penalty Points Guide'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/97_Driving Offences - Road Traffic Offences - Penalty Points Guide.pdf?1409044964" target="_blank">Driving Offences and Penalties</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Personal Injury</span></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Making A Claim'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/106_Personal Injury V2.pdf?1418042037" target="_blank">Making a Claim</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Defending Claims'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/112_DefendingClaims.pdf?1418382223" target="_blank">Defending Claims</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Road Traffic Accidents'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/107_Road Traffic.pdf?1418042070" target="_blank">Road Traffic Accident Claims</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Defective Products'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/111_DefectiveProducts.pdf?1418382196" target="_blank">Defective Products Claims</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Medical Negligence'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/114_MedicalNegligence.pdf?1418382277" target="_blank">Medical Negligence Claims</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Work Related Illness'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/113_WorkRelatedIllness.pdf?1418382248" target="_blank">Work Related Illness Claims</a></p>\r\n<p>Guide to <a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Slips &amp; Trips'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/108_Slips and Trips.pdf?1418042106" target="_blank">Slips and Trips Claims</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2010-11-12 17:05:12', '2015-07-22 11:41:52', '', '', 1, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>96% of our clients would recommend us to a friend</p>\r\n<p>Why not tell us what you think?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '92_iStock_000009311779XSmall.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 112950, '2011-03-22 16:31:04', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '');
