(18, 'Who We Support', 'who_we_support', 'Social Responsibility', 18, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p style="text-align: left;">As a business we feel that it is important to give something back to the communities within which we work and, as such, we regularly participate in charitable events and fundraisers.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We work with several charities across Derbyshire and South Yorkshire and regularly raise money for the national fundraising events.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1 style="text-align: left;">Some of&nbsp;our&nbsp;fundraising:</h1>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">March 2015- Endurer Dash</h2>\r\n<p><span>On Saturday 28th March the Banner Jones &ldquo;Mud Loving Legals&rdquo; set off to&nbsp;</span><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?ll=53.289338,-1.548293&amp;z=14&amp;t=h&amp;hl=en-US&amp;gl=US&amp;mapclient=embed&amp;q=Holmesfield+Dronfield,+Derbyshire+S18+7WE+UK&amp;output=classic&amp;dg=brw" target="_blank">Barlow</a><span>&nbsp;in the Peak District to take on the&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.endurerevents.co.uk/endurer-dash-8km-race-schedule/" target="_blank">Endurer 8km Dash</a>&nbsp;in support of<span><em>&nbsp;</em><a href="http://www.googleadservices.com/pagead/aclk?sa=L&amp;ai=C90PigTYZVfOSDOOojAa3nYCoA_-ZkIoEz6DuxzXHl52PFQgAEAFgu76ug9AKoAGd_6T8A8gBAaoEHE_QA47N1zX5sN4W94xYkXiHHqq91C25WMsI88aIBgGAB8uA2wOQBwOoB6a-G9gHAQ&amp;ohost=www.google.co.uk&amp;cid=5GiJXp_NKprZHLqBGhktbippSm4UA_ncqI8iIwbP1h4CTYgN&amp;sig=AOD64_0NJsY0c7eKZdnP9zL07z5bqJc8HA&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;ved=0CB8Q0Qw&amp;adurl=http://www.helpforheroes.org.uk" target="_blank">Help for Heroes</a><em>.</em></span></p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;"><img src="../../..//assets/page_contents/18/contained_images/b680ac3d4b76_420_FullSizeRender.jpg?1427715527" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="250" /></h2>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">February 2015- Clothing Collection</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">During the month of February we asked our staff to clear out their wardrobes and donate all of their unwanted clothes to Ashgate Hospice.&nbsp; The clothing collection will &nbsp;help Ashgate Hospice&nbsp;&nbsp;raise urgent funds by providing stock for their shops.&nbsp;&nbsp; We helped them by donating almost 20 bags of clothing!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;<img src="../../../assets/page_contents/18/contained_images/51477d554815_403_SAM_0571.JPG?1424267915" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="170" height="217" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">December 2014- Christmas Jumper Day</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">On the 12th December 2014 our staff wore Christmas Jumpers to work and helped us to raise over &pound;170 for Save the Children.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Here''s the proof!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="../../../assets/page_contents/18/contained_images/11e9a0805420_402_24GG2.jpg?1424267426" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">September 2014- Chesterfield Marathon&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">On September 14th Chesterfield hosted it''s first every Marathon.&nbsp; We entered an all girl team in the relay event and the girls finished 8th out of the 35 relay teams that entered!&nbsp;&nbsp; As well as having a lot of fun we managed to raise a total of &pound;219.43 for the Chesterfield Kids n Cancer charity.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="../../../assets/page_contents/18/contained_images/6687371c4ea8_358_Chesterfield Marathon 2014.jpg?1411466182" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">December 2013 - Autoworld Toy Appeal</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">In December we decided that we would collect as many toys together as we could for the Autoworld Toy appeal. This is a local project that collects together brand new toys and gives them out to local children''s charities.&nbsp; All of the staff were incredibily generous and we sent several bags of toys down to the appeal.&nbsp; Here we are presenting our toys to Autoworld along with Sean and Becky from the Peak fm breakfast show.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="../../../assets/page_contents/18/contained_images/2fac30d85e7f_236_bj peak and autoworld.jpg?1389621876" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="308" height="203" /></p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Ashgate Hospice Spooktacular 2013</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="../../../assets/page_contents/18/contained_images/821dfcbc90d1_226_final result.JPG?1383236871" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="255" height="311" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Executive Director Chris Sellars agreed to have his face painted by Becky Measures (host of Peak fm''s Breakfast show) on halloween to raise money for&nbsp; Ashgate Hopice.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; We''re still not sure if it has come off!</p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Fund raising for Children with Cancer UK July 2013</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">During July <a href="../../../team_members/42">Toby Netting</a>, Director and Family Solicitor &nbsp;will be taking part in a super challenge, running, cycling or rowing&nbsp;10K&nbsp;every day for all of July.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">The total distance covered over the month will be 310K or just over 192 miles. The charity helps children deal with all types of cancer and also helps support their parents. If you want an insight in to what sort of decisions are involved, please check out this blog&nbsp;about a boy with leukaemia &nbsp;<a href="http://henryteam.wordpress.com/">http://henryteam.wordpress.com</a> .</p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Three Peaks Challenge July 2013</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">A&nbsp; team from Banner Jones are attempting to conquer the Yorkshire Three Peaks Challenge, a staggering 25 miles in 12 hours on 27th July 2013 to help raise funds for The Stroke Association.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">If you would like to sponsor the team please follow the link below. <a href="http://www.justgiving.com/Banner-Jonesthreepeaks">http://www.justgiving.com/Banner-Jonesthreepeaks</a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Race for Life 2013</strong></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">A team of ladies from Banner Jones recently took part in the Chesterfield Race for Life raising money for Breast Cancer Research.</p>\r\n<h1 style="text-align: left;"><img src="../../../assets/page_contents/18/contained_images/5c1df068ee51_191_Race for Life 16th June 2013.jpg?1374054273" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></h1>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Bargain Hunt Challenge 2011</strong></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">A team from Banner Jones recently&nbsp; took part in the annual Bargain Hunt challenge which is part of the Chesterfield''s arts and market festival.&nbsp; Each team were given &pound;100 which they had to spend on items from the antiques market.&nbsp; The items were then judged and valued by TV''s ''Cash in the attic'' and ''Antiques Roadshow'' Jonty Hearnden.&nbsp;&nbsp;He claimed that our items would make the most profit and auction and on the basis the Banner Jones team were declared the winners of the challenge.&nbsp;&nbsp; Here is Jonty handing over our winnings which we decided we would donate to the local Bluebell Wood Children''s Hospice.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="../../../assets/page_contents/18/contained_images/55bc7d254388_134_133_Jonty_and_Winners.JPG?1320396349" border="0" alt="Jonty and the winners" hspace="0" width="250" /></p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Great Yorkshire Run Business Challenge 2011</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">The Banner Jones running team came back with a vengeance in this year&rsquo;s 10k Bupa Great Yorkshire run in Sheffield.&nbsp; The Banner Jones mixed team won the Medium sized Business Challenge for the second consecutive year.&nbsp; As well as having a lot of fun along the way, we used the event as a way to raise money for the national charity &lsquo;Voice&rsquo; who support the&nbsp;thousands of vulnerable children in the UK care system.&nbsp; &nbsp;As well as the sponsorship from the race Banner Jones have held other fundraising events including a dress down day for staff, raising over &pound;400 which will go towards the inspiring work they do here in our region&rsquo;.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="../../../assets/page_contents/18/contained_images/c4675f570d43_132_team on sofa.JPG?1320159348" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Three Peaks Challenge</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Chris Sellars, Executive Director and Head of Business Legal Services took part in the 3 Peaks Challenge in June 2011.&nbsp; The 3 Peaks Challenge involves climbing Snowdon, Scafell Pike and Ben Nevis in just 24 hours!&nbsp; The team of 14 who took part in this years challenge raised a total of &pound;13,000 for the Masonic Samaritans Fund.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="../../../assets/page_contents/18/contained_images/d74afd0261c2_122_chris 3 peaks.JPG?1310736209" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="209" height="175" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">This is Chris regretting his choice of footwear!</p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Woolly Hat Day</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Some of the braver members of staff donned their woolly hats to support the Cathedral Archer homeless project in Sheffield Feb 2011</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="../../../assets/page_contents/18/contained_images/522cbdef573f_111_sheffield.jpg?1299252746" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="205" height="143" /></p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Great Yorkshire Run 2010</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Seven keen runners take part in the Great Yorkshire 10K run (Business Challenge) in aid of Weston Park Cancer Charity, September 2010, and they won!&nbsp; Some of them are keen to do it again this year...</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp; <img src="../../../assets/page_contents/18/contained_images/fa5513ce3a20_12_WestonParkEvent_2.jpg?1295267776" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="185" height="127" /></p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Drag Race 2010</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">The Spice Girls reunited at the Ashgate Hospice Drag Race May 2010</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="../../../assets/page_contents/18/contained_images/5db3e17c4b0e_10_HospiceEvent_2.jpg?1295267628" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="185" height="142" /></p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Question Time fundraising event 2010</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Cheque presentations to Ashgate Hospice (left) and Weston Park&nbsp;(right) &nbsp;following our charity ''Question Time'' event Feb 2010</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="../../../assets/page_contents/18/contained_images/030e6c754a7a_9_HospiceEvent_1.jpg?1295267612" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="168" height="105" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="../../../assets/page_contents/18/contained_images/34aa1c0f0cae_11_WestonParkEvent_1.jpg?1295267763" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="179" height="111" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>', '2010-11-12 17:07:34', '2015-03-30 11:53:53', '', '', 1, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>Leaving a gift to charity in your Will can be very satisfying</p>\r\n<p>Ask us about this today</p>', '94_iStock_000009588868XSmall.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 47717, '2011-03-04 15:34:49', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '/page/legacies', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, ''),
(19, 'Why Choose Banner Jones?', 'why_choose_banner_jones', 'Why Choose Banner Jones?', 19, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p>We are confident that we can provide specialist legal advice to suit your needs and we want to be your first choice legal adviser.</p>\r\n<p>We pride ourselves on the quality of our&nbsp;service and that''s why:</p>\r\n<p>96% of our&nbsp;clients would recommend us to a friend&nbsp;(ongoing client survey).</p>\r\n<p>Here are some other reasons to let us help you:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>We&rsquo;ll offer you a Fixed Fee wherever possible so you&rsquo;ll know exactly what you&rsquo;re paying upfront</li>\r\n<li>Our solicitors/Advisers are experts in their areas of law with many having additional legal accreditations</li>\r\n<li>We cover a large geographic area, so whether you''re looking for a solicitor in Sheffield, Chesterfield or Dronfield, we''re close by.</li>\r\n<li>We care about you as our client and we hold a Customer Service award&nbsp;to prove it! ( Derbyshire Times, Customer Service Award 2010)</li>\r\n<li>We won an Excellence in Professional Services award in 2013</li>\r\n<li>We were entered into the Legal 500 rankings in 2013 and 2014</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Our Promise to you:</p>\r\n<p>We will endeavour to adhere to various service standards during the time we are acting for you. In particular:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>We will keep you regularly informed of the progress of your matter</li>\r\n<li>We will communicate in plain language</li>\r\n<li>We will explain&nbsp;the work&nbsp;that may be required</li>\r\n<li>We will advise you of the likely timescale involved</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Important Note: We have a legal duty to release information about money laundering and Solicitors also have a duty to the Court. These duties will always override the duty of confidentiality or the requirement to put your interests first.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2010-11-12 17:08:55', '2014-12-23 14:40:45', '', '', 1, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>With over&nbsp;140 staff we''ve got it covered, so your case will always stay on track</p>', '54_iStock_000001364064XSmall.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 179160, '2011-03-04 14:55:49', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '/page/about-us', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, ''),
(20, '<span class="business">Services for <span>your business</span></span>', 'services_for_your_business', 'Business Legal Services', 20, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2>Your real business partner</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We&rsquo;re with you every step of the way&hellip; Whether it&rsquo;s starting up a business, running a business or exiting a business our specialist team can help.</p>\r\n<p>We have acted in all transactions from small business transfers to multimillion pound mergers, acquisitions and disposals.&nbsp; Some of our clients include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Chesterfield Football Club</li>\r\n<li>Rotherham Rugby Union Football Club</li>\r\n<li>Chesterfield Borough Council</li>\r\n<li>Chesterfield College</li>\r\n<li>Chesterfield Precision Engineering</li>\r\n<li>Derbyshire County Council</li>\r\n<li>Derbyshire Primary Care Trust</li>\r\n<li>Derbyshire Fire Service</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Many businesses hate the uncertainty of what the solicitor&rsquo;s fee will be. With the Banner Jones Fixed Fee promise you can be reassured that wherever possible you will know exactly what you are going to pay for your work upfront. Refreshing?</p>\r\n<p><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, contact our specialist Business Legal Services team on <span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span>* or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjones.co.uk">info@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>', '2010-11-12 17:09:20', '2015-03-19 14:28:34', '', '', 1, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>We are a leading firm in the Legal 500</p>', '359_UK_leading_firm_2014.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 7199, '2014-10-02 14:32:42', '', 'family_highlight', '75_iStock_000005717962XSmall.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 204931, '2011-05-06 14:55:37', 'Alt Tag -- Can be controlled through the Admin', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<p>Example Content Set-up to demonstrate functionality to Chris Coney.</p>\r\nThis is the "Spash Page" Content that can be controlled through the admin<br />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Banner Content - Can be controlled through the Admin', '', '', '', 7, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 1, '', '', ''),
(21, '<span class="family">Services for <span>you & your family</span></span>', 'services_for_you_and_your_family', 'Bringing Family Law to Life', 21, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="../../../page/pre-or-postmarital-partnership-agreements"></a>You may never know when you are going to need the services of a solicitor, but one thing is for sure, you will need one at some point in your life. When this point arises you need to be&nbsp;confident that you''re "in good hands".</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">With Banner Jones, you can be assured that not only will you receive specialist legal advice but&nbsp; that the&nbsp;advice will be provided in a way which is easy to understand, making your matter as stress free as possible.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We want to help and guide you through all of life&rsquo;s little challenges.&nbsp; We''re bringing law to life....to your life</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Through the good times...</p>\r\n<ul style="text-align: left;">\r\n<li>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><a href="../../../page/pre-or-postmarital-partnership-agreements">Getting married</a></div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><a href="../../../page/residential-property">Moving house</a></div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/making-a-will">Having a baby</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">And the bad...</p>\r\n<ul style="text-align: left;">\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/divorce-and-separation">Relationship broken down</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/personal-injury">Had an accident</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/probate-and-estates">Lost a loved one</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Instructing a solicitor can often be a daunting task especially when you sometimes have no idea how much it will cost you. With the Banner Jones <a href="../../../page/fixed-fee-promise">Fixed Fee promise </a>you can be reassured that wherever possible you will know exactly what you are going to pay for your work upfront. Refreshing?</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="../../../page/about-us">Read more about us</a>. Banner Jones have various office locations, so whether you need a solicitor in Sheffield, Chesterfield or Dronfield, we''re sure to be close by.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, call</strong>&nbsp;<strong><span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span></strong><span>*</span></strong><strong>&nbsp;or email <a href="mailto:info@bannerjones.co.uk">info@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><span>*</span><span><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></span><br /></strong></p>', '2010-11-12 17:09:42', '2015-02-10 15:36:34', '', '', 1, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>We are a Leading Firm in the Legal 500 UK</p>', '359_UK_leading_firm_2014.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 7199, '2015-01-05 09:25:37', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'Family.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 43061, '2011-01-11 11:46:57', 'Family', '', '', 'Family', '', '', 9, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(23, 'Company Formation', 'company_formation', 'Company Formation', 23, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2>Build a solid foundation</h2>\r\n<p>Here are some things that you will need to consider carefully during the formation of your business.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The company structure, Sole Trader, LLP or Ltd company?</li>\r\n<li>The choice of Company name.&nbsp; Your trading/brand name may be different to your registered company name for tax purposes.</li>\r\n<li>The preparation of memorandum and Articles of Association</li>\r\n<li>The buying of the Company</li>\r\n<li>The registering of Domain Names for websites</li>\r\n<li>Sorting out the Company Secretary and Directors. With Directors Duties and Liabilities becoming more onerous all the time it is vital that the relevant Companies and Insolvency Legislation is complied with.</li>\r\n<li>The issue of Share Capital.</li>\r\n<li>Protecting your Intellectual Property. We can help you apply for patents or registration marks if required.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>It isn&rsquo;t always new companies who need advice on Company Formation, often we see Companies involved in mergers, takeovers, management buyouts and purchasers that need to ensure the change is structured in the best way possible. As part of this we can advise on share transfers and restructuring.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, contact our specialist Business Legal Services team on&nbsp;<span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span>*&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjones.co.uk">info@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>', '2010-11-12 17:10:44', '2015-03-19 14:20:43', '', '', 1, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>Had a bright idea that you want to protect?</p>\r\n<p>Click here for more information</p>', '109_iStock_000015062565XSmall.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 74086, '2011-03-25 12:55:48', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'CompanyFormation.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 43914, '2010-12-22 09:23:20', 'Company Formation', '', '', 'Company Formation', '/page/intellectual-property-protection', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '/page/intellectual-property-protection', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(24, 'Commercial Agreements', 'commercial_agreements', 'Commercial Agreements', 24, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2 style="text-align: left;">It''s all in the detail</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We would always advise that you check any commercial agreements thoroughly at the start of any business venture and if you&rsquo;re not sure where to start, we&rsquo;re here to help every step of the way.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We can assist in drafting and advising on all types of commercial contracts including the following:-</p>\r\n<ul style="text-align: left;">\r\n<li>Partnership agreements, including limited liability partnership</li>\r\n<li>Company acquisitions</li>\r\n<li>Shareholders agreements</li>\r\n<li>Joint venture agreements </li>\r\n<li>Terms and conditions</li>\r\n<li>Franchise, agency, or distribution agreements</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We will always take account of the commercial realities that your business faces and help you to review and discuss any difficult issues. The important this is that your agreements protect your business in the best way possible which is why we will always tailor them to your individual business.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, contact our specialist Business Legal Services team on&nbsp;<span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span>*&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjones.co.uk">info@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes</sub></strong></p>', '2010-11-12 17:11:00', '2015-03-19 14:25:33', '', '', 1, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>If you have commercial agreements with businesses abroad we have a notary who can help you</p>', '102_iStock_000012393462XSmall.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 57204, '2011-03-29 14:48:38', '', 'business_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'CommercialAgreements.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 34770, '2010-12-22 09:20:40', 'Commercial Agreements', '', '', 'Commercial Agreements', '/page/notary', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '/page/notary', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(25, 'Dispute Resolution', 'dispute_resolution', 'Commercial Disputes', 25, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2>We''ll sort it</h2>\r\n<p>If you have any kind of commercial dispute, we can help you to resolve it.&nbsp;&nbsp; There are various ways we can do this and we&rsquo;ll advise you on the best course of action to suit your case whether it is through negotiation, <a href="http://www.midlandsmediation.co.uk/civil-commercial-mediation/" target="_blank">mediation</a>, arbitration, or litigation.</p>\r\n<p>We have wide experience of:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Contract disputes</li>\r\n<li><a href="http://www.midlandsmediation.co.uk/civil-commercial-mediation/" target="_blank">Commercial Mediation</a></li>\r\n<li>Partnership disputes</li>\r\n<li>Professional Negligence</li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/debt-recovery-business">Debt recovery</a></li>\r\n<li>Liability issues and other commercial problems</li>\r\n<li>We also act on landlord and tenant matters including             \r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Rent review and service charge disputes</li>\r\n<li>Repair and dilapidations</li>\r\n<li>Breaches of covenants</li>\r\n<li>Lease renewals</li>\r\n<li>Possession actions.&nbsp; </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, contact our expert&nbsp;Commercial Dispute Resolution team on&nbsp;<span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span>*&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjones.co.uk">info@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>', '2010-11-12 17:11:26', '2015-03-19 14:26:45', '', '', 1, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>Losing money from bad tenants?</p>\r\n<p>We can help you</p>\r\n<p>NEW&nbsp;FIXED FEE LANDLORD ASSIST</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '83_iStock_000007854419XSmall.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 99712, '2011-03-30 10:47:41', '', 'business_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'DisputeResolution.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 50718, '2010-12-22 09:24:46', 'Dispute Resolution', '', '', 'Dispute Resolution', '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(26, 'Commercial Property', 'commercial_property', 'Commercial Property', 26, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p>Whether you are starting a business, expanding your business or looking to dispose of your business then it&rsquo;s likely that you will need commercial property advice at some point. Our local experienced team will get to know your business and ensure that our advice is tailored to your individual needs. There will often be things to consider that you may not have even thought about.</p>\r\n<p>When looking for business premises you may be uncertain about whether to buy your premises or maybe look at leasing long term. We can talk you through the pro&rsquo;s and con&rsquo;s for each option and guide you through them step by step.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;We can help you with:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The sale and purchase of offices and retail outlets</li>\r\n<li>Acquisition requirements such as finding and funding larger business premises </li>\r\n<li>The disposal of your business and it&rsquo;s property</li>\r\n<li>The development and/or disposal of plots</li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/landlord-or-tenant-disputes">Landlord and tenant issues</a></li>\r\n<li>Granting of leases</li>\r\n<li>Tenancy agreements</li>\r\n<li>Green Leases. read our <a href="../../../articles/24" target="_blank">free guide</a></li>\r\n<li>Contested leases.&nbsp; Our commercial <a href="../../../page/dispute-resolution">dispute resolution</a> team can advise on other contentious issues arising out of commercial property.</li>\r\n<li>Buying and selling commercial <a href="../../../page/notary">property abroad</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/notary">Notary Services</a>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, contact our specialist Business Legal Services team on&nbsp;<span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span>*&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjones.co.uk">info@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>', '2010-11-12 17:11:44', '2015-03-19 14:23:11', '', '', 1, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>Give your business some TLC</p>\r\n<p>Legal support with a fixed montly cost.</p>\r\n<p>FREE employment healthcheck included</p>', '110_tlc.JPG', 'image/jpeg', 18257, '2011-03-29 15:17:21', '', 'business_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'CommercialProperty.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 57211, '2010-12-22 09:22:52', 'Commercial Property', '', '', 'Commercial Property', '/page/total-legal-care-insurance', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '/page/total-legal-care-insurance', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(27, 'Employment Law', 'employment', 'Employment Law Business', 27, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">Employment law is constantly changing and dealing with HR and employment law issues can be one of the most difficult factors in running your business or organisation.</span></p>\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s therefore crucial to ensure that you get the right advice at the right time to ensure that you keep on track. The Employment Law specialists at Banner Jones have many years experience advising and guiding employers to ensure that they get the best outcome for them. We can guide you through the entire life cycle of the employment relationship from recruitment to termination, and can offer advice on:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/discipline-and-grievance">Disciplinary and Grievance</a> matters</li>\r\n<li>Handling <a href="../../../page/redundancies-and-reorganisations">Redundancies and Reorganisations</a> </li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/business-transfers-and-tupe">Business Transfers and TUPE</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/discrimination-in-the-workplace">Discrimination in the Workplace</a> </li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/family-friendly-rights-business">Family Friendly Rights</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; </li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/contracts-and-staff-handbooks">Contracts of Employment and Staff Handbooks</a> </li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/restrictive-covenants-business">Restrictive Covenants</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/employment-tribunals-business">Employment Tribunals</a> </li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/settlement-agreements-business">Settlement (Compromise) Agreements</a></li>\r\n<li>HR Services</li>\r\n<li>Training </li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/workplace-mediation-business">Mediation</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/employer-assist">Employer Assist</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>For more information regarding any employment or HR issues,