im. Once litigation action has been instigated you will be liable to discharge all Legal fees whether we are successful or not. In the instance recovery is obtained from the debtor, the Legal fees recovered will duly be credited to you.</sub></p>\r\n<p><sub>** Alternative enforcement procedures are available and advice and costings can be supplied on request.</sub></p>\r\n<p><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, contact our specialist Business Legal Services team on&nbsp;<span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span>*&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjones.co.uk">info@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>', '2010-11-12 17:13:46', '2015-03-25 15:27:28', '', '', 1, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>Track the progress of your debt collections on line with our new Debt Interactive</p>\r\n<p>LOG IN HERE</p>', '86_iStock_000008332115XSmall.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 52852, '2011-03-30 10:49:05', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'DebtRecovery.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 49439, '2010-12-22 09:24:14', 'Debt Recovery', '', '', 'Debt Recovery', '', 'https://www.bannerjones-debtrecovery.co.uk', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
