(31, 'Corporate Crime', 'corporate_crime', 'Corporate Crime', 31, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2>Are you under the spotlight?</h2>\r\n<p>This can be a very worrying time for the manager and staff of a business and we know you&rsquo;ll need a legal partner who has experience in this field and can guide you through it step by step.&nbsp; We deal with emergency situations on a daily basis and are experienced in defending companies being prosecuted for every type of offence. Whether the matter relates to your premises or the protection of staff or customers we can advise and defend you.</p>\r\n<p>Some of our areas of expertise include</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Health &amp; Safety breaches</li>\r\n<li>Trading Standards </li>\r\n<li>Environmental Law</li>\r\n<li>Fraud and Financial Crime Investigation</li>\r\n<li>Regulatory Offences</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Whatever the problem our lawyers will go through your case with you and give you an honest opinion of the likely outcome.</p>\r\n<p>When faced with serious business issues such as this, would it benefit you to know you could just pick up the phone to an experienced commercial lawyer without incurring an additional charge?&nbsp; With a fixed cost monthly retainer from <a href="../../../page/total-legal-care-insurance">Total Legal Care</a>, we&rsquo;ll give you business and employment law advice whenever you need it at no additional cost.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, contact our specialist Business Legal Services team on&nbsp;<span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span>*&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjones.co.uk">info@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>', '2010-11-12 17:14:38', '2015-03-19 14:21:39', '', '', 1, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>Let us help you stay on the right side of the law for an affordable fixed monthly cost</p>', '110_