(79, 'Dispute Resolution', 'dispute_resolution__family', 'Dispute resolution', 79, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2 style="text-align: left;">Are you involved in a dispute?</h2>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">We''re with you every step of the way...</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">The types of disputes we see on a day to day basis are extremely varied, but we know that every client who comes to see has the same question on their mind &ndash; do I have a case?&nbsp; Our team of experts will help and guide you through your case and let you know the likely outcome from the start.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We recognise the importance of keeping dispute cases out of court so wherever possible we will always avoid litigation, but if required we will fight fearlessly for your rights.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>If you think you have a dispute case and want to have a chat with a specialist solicitor, please contact us by phone on&nbsp;</strong><strong><span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span></strong>*<strong>&nbsp;or via email at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjones.co.uk">info@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>', '2010-11-15 11:03:37', '2015-02-10 15:51:09', '', '', 1, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>Are you a private landlord with several properties?</p>\r\n<p>Had problems with rent collection and evictions?</p>\r\n<p>Let us help you</p>', '105_iStock_000013135809XSmall.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 249179, '2011-03-04 16:39:03', 'dispute resolution solicitors chesterfield', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'DisputeResolution.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 50597, '2010-12-22 09:43:32', 'Dispute Resolution', '', '', 'Dispute Resolution', '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(80, 'Employment Law', 'employment_disputes', 'Employment Law', 80, 0, 0, 0, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2 style="text-align: justify;">Problems at work?</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Employment law changes more rapidly than any other area of the law, which is why if you think you have an issue it&rsquo;s best to seek advice as soon as possible.&nbsp; We&rsquo;re here to put your mind at ease and make sure that your rights as an employee are upheld. If you have an employment problem, quite often there maybe something else for consideration within your case so it&rsquo;s always worth finding out for certain.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We can advise you on the legal rights to which you are entitled &ndash; whether they relate to disciplinary proceedings, maternity rights, discrimination, redundancy, applications to Employment Tribunals, or any other disputes.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Often the right advice at the right time can lead to matters being resolved with the minimum of stress to you.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">For more information on <a href="http://http//www.lawdonut.co.uk/law/employment-law/?s=BAN082" target="_blank">employment law</a> why not visit our FREE legal resource centre?</p>', '2010-11-15 11:04:16', '2014-01-23 17:13:42', '', '', 1, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>For the latest updates in employment law why not visit our FREE legal resource centre?</p>', '71_iStock_000004583601XSmall.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 108950, '2013-02-25 16:26:56', 'employment law solicitors chesterfield', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'EmploymentDisputes.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 51721, '2010-12-22 09:44:02', 'Employment Disputes', '', '', 'Employment Disputes', '', 'http://www.lawdonut.co.uk/?s=ban082', 4, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '<p><a href="http://http//www.bannerjones.co.uk/assets/stored_documents/original/45_Banner Jones Employment Assist Leaflet.pdf?1389792596" target="_blank">Download Banner Jones Employment Assist PDF</a></p>\r\n<p><img src="../../../assets/stored_images/original/237_employment assist.jpg?1389800538" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="250" /></p>', NULL, NULL),
(81, 'Consumer Disputes', 'consumer_disputes__dispute_resolution', 'Problem with a faulty product?', 81, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p style="text-align: left;">If you have a problem with goods you have purchased, we may be able to negotiate a satisfactory resolution. If necessary, we will act for you in enforcing your rights through the courts.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Our experience covers many types of dispute. Typical examples are:</p>\r\n<ul style="text-align: left;">\r\n<li>faulty cars and other goods which are not satisfactory</li>\r\n<li>hire purchase and credit agreements for unsatisfactory goods</li>\r\n<li>faulty or incomplete work by builders or other tradesmen</li>\r\n<li>unfair consumer contracts</li>\r\n<li>holidays that do not match their description in a brochure</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, call <span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span></strong>*<strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjones.co.uk">info@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>', '2010-11-15 11:04:55', '2015-03-19 11:48:45', '', '', 1, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>Do you know what your rights are?</p>\r\n<p>Click here for a full list of consumer rights</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '52_iStock_000000751879XSmall.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 147335, '2011-03-04 16:40:23', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'ConsumerDisputes.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 51918, '2011-01-12 14:30:04', 'Consumer Disputes', '', '', 'Consumer Disputes', '', 'http://www.consumerdirect.gov.uk/after_you_buy/know-your-rights/', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(82, 'Property Disputes', 'property_disputes', 'Problem with a boundary?', 82, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p style="text-align: left;">Property disputes can be very stressful as they often arise when a building job has not been completed properly or maybe you are rowing with a neighbour over a boundary fence?&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Our expertise in the complex area of building disputes applies a sound commercial approach to achieving a resolution whether you are an individual, or a construction company.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Starting with the contract you entered into, we identify the essential elements of the dispute.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We can help you with claims concerning:</p>\r\n<ul style="text-align: left;">\r\n<li>Failure to carry out or complete building work</li>\r\n<li>Defective construction</li>\r\n<li>Disputes over costs</li>\r\n<li>Boundary disputes on your land</li>\r\n<li>Ownership disputes </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We can act either in the defence of the building company, or for individuals and businesses that are in dispute with builders</p>\r\n<p>We can also advise you in creating a professional contract with a builder at the start of a job so that if things turn bad you have a legally binding contract to fall back on.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, call <span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span></strong>*<strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjones.co.uk">info@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>', '2010-11-15 11:05:28', '2015-03-19 11:49:01', '', '', 1, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>Planning an extension?&nbsp; Get a legally binding contract in place with your builder.</p>\r\n<p>It''s better to be safe than sorry</p>', '60_iStock_000001722438XSmall.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 93059, '2011-03-24 16:47:37', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'PropertyDisputes.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 44851, '2010-12-22 10:11:43', 'Property Disputes', '', '', 'Property Disputes', '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(83, 'Landlord/Tenant Disputes', 'land_lord_or_tenant_disputes', 'Landlord and Tenant Disputes', 83, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2>Frustrated with bad tenants?</h2>\r\n<p>If you are a landord of private residential property then you may be suffering with bad tenants.</p>\r\n<p>Our expert dispute resolution team&nbsp;in Chesterfield can advise on the problems of either landlords or tenants. We combine our knowledge of this specialised area of law with practical advice.</p>\r\n<h2>Landlord Assist</h2>\r\n<p>With our<strong> Landlord Assist </strong>scheme&nbsp;we can act&nbsp;for you on a FIXED FEE basis, helping you to reach a quick and effective resolution. The&nbsp;scheme&nbsp;will help you to budget as you will know the exact cost at the start of the proceedings.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Some of the typical problems on which we advise are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Possession proceedings-processing the matter from the initial notice to eviction if necessary.</li>\r\n<li>Recovery of Rent Arrears</li>\r\n<li>Claims relating to protection of deposits</li>\r\n<li>Disrepair claims</li>\r\n<li>Breach of tenancy conditions</li>\r\n<li>Nuisance behaviour</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>If your tenants are not paying rent, or for some other reason you want recover possession of your property, then we can assit you with all the steps from serving notices up to and including representing you at court hearings. Each stage is set at a FIXED FEE.</p>\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="163" valign="top">\r\n<p><strong><em>Stage</em></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p><strong><em>Our Costs</em></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p><strong><em>Vat</em></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p><strong><em>Court Fees</em></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p><strong><em>Total Cost for Stage</em></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="163" valign="top">\r\n<p>Serving Notice Seeking Possession</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p>&pound;150.00</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p>&pound;30.00</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p>n/a</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p>&pound;180.00</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="163" valign="top">\r\n<p>Possession Proceedings</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p>&pound;315.00</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p>&pound;63.00</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p>&pound;280.00</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p>&pound;658.00</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="163" valign="top">\r\n<p>Warrant for Possession</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p>&pound;140.00</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p>&pound;28.00</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p>&pound;110.00</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p>&pound;278.00</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="163" valign="top">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="163" valign="top">\r\n<p>TOTAL FIXED FEE</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="101" valign="top">\r\n<p>&pound;1,116.00</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>For advice on Tenant Deposits <a href="../../../articles/220" target="_blank">click here</a></p>\r\n<h2>Tenants</h2>\r\n<p>If the property you rent is in disrepair, or you are suffering harassment or unlawful eviction, we can advise you on your rights and take legal action against your landlord where appropriate.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, call <span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span></strong>*<strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjones.co.uk">info@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>', '2010-11-15 11:06:08', '2015-03-19 11:49:13', '', '', 1, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>Ease your stress with our</p>\r\n<p>Fixed Fee Landlord Assist package</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '105_iStock_000013135809XSmall.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 249179, '2011-03-04 16:42:07', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'LandlordDisputes.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 65876, '2010-12-22 17:12:06', 'Landlord/Tenant Disputes', '', '', 'Landlord/Tenant Disputes', '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(84, 'Wills, Trusts and Estate Disputes', 'wills_trusts_and_estate_disputes', 'Contesting a Will', 84, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2 style="text-align: left;">We can help you get your rightful share</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Wills by their very nature can be contentious and often certain family members who have been neglected in the Will may wish to challenge other beneficiaries to get what they believe is their rightful share.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">If you would like more information about contesting a Will, our specialists can tell you the sorts of things that can be looked at in ruling a Will invalid.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Taking steps to rule a Will invalid can be a very lengthy and drawn out process so we always advise that families think carefully about this before taking such action to avoid irriversible rifts in the family.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For more information about contesting a Will, or to arrange an appointment, call <span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span></strong>*<strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjones.co.uk">info@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>', '2010-11-15 11:06:46', '2015-03-19 11:49:26', '', '', 1, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>Speak to our Contentious Wills expert:</p>\r\n<p>Rob Stubbs</p>', '190_Rob stubbs new.JPG', 'image/jpeg', 33867, '2013-06-07 10:54:34', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'WillsTrustsAndEstateDisputes.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 54254, '2011-01-13 14:56:52', 'Wills, Trusts and Estate disputes', '', '', 'Wills, Trusts and Estate disputes', '/team_members/31', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '<p>To avoid this happening to your family, make sure your Will is up to date and provides for everyone you want it to</p>\r\n<p>Review your Will now</p>', '/team_members/31', '', '49_wom with baby.JPG', 'image/jpeg', 185944, '2013-06-07 10:55:43', '', 0, '', '', ''),
(85, 'Debt Recovery', 'debt_recovery__family', 'Debt Recovery ', 85, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2 style="text-align: left;">Need to recover a debt? We can help you.</h2>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Sometimes a letter from a solicitor is all it takes ...</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">If you have a problem collecting money owed to you, we have the expertise to help. We will pursue your debts as quickly as possible in a cost-effective way, combining our knowledge and experience with our specialist case management software.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">If the debtor does not pay the debt quickly, we will consult you on how far to pursue it and whether to litigate. If a court order is obtained and the debtor still fails to pay, we will enforce payment by the most appropriate means. Throughout the process, we will keep you informed.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">In some cases it is appropriate to consider bankruptcy proceedings against an individual, or winding-up proceedings if the debtor is a company. We will discuss these options with you to ensure the best possible outcome.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment,</strong></strong><strong>&nbsp;call <span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span></strong>*<strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjones.co.uk">info@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><br /></strong></p>\r\n<h1 style="text-align: left;">Our Fixed Fee debt collection&nbsp;service is a really cost effective way for you to collect debts owing to you</h1>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Stage 1</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Send a Solicitors Letter before action an