(92, 'Slander', 'defarmation_and_slander', 'Slander', 92, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p>In recent months we have a rise in slander cases. This means that someone believes something bad has been said against them and they want to fight to clear their name.</p>', '2010-12-08 13:57:06', '2011-01-21 15:42:18', '', '', 1, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'Slander.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 36578, '2010-12-22 10:16:20', 'Defamation and Slander', '', '', 'Defamation and Slander', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL);
