(114, 'Lasting Power of Attorney', 'lasting_power_of_attorney_elderly_services', 'Lasting Power of Attorney', 114, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p style="text-align: left;">There may be a variety of reasons why you might need to look after someone else&rsquo;s affairs and there are several ways of ensuring that you are acting properly on their behalf.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">A Lasting Power of Attorney (or LPA) is created to allow someone else the ability to look after your affairs if your mental capacity is lost. More often than not people create Lasting Powers of Attorney in later life when there is a higher chance of mental capacity being lost through dementia for example.&nbsp; However, mental capacity can be lost at any age as a result of say, an accident so we would also advise anyone with complex financial affairs to have one as well.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">At Banner Jones we can advise you on the best course of action for your particular circumstances.</p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">One of our most frequent questions would be:</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">My father is elderly and has said that he would prefer me to deal with his bills and finances for him. Can I do this?</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">As long as your father has mental capacity he could do this by giving you &ldquo;power of attorney&rdquo; which will allow you to look after things for up to a year for him. If he later loses mental capacity, however, then the power of attorney will come to an end.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Alternatively, your father could give you Lasting Power of Attorney (LPA). This would not come to an end if your father were to lose mental capacity later on, and will last indefinitely, not just for one year. We would need to see your father personally so we can explain the LPA to him and make sure this is what he wants. We would then be able to prepare a document for him to sign, which would give you power to deal with his finances on his behalf.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We will tailor-make the LPA to suit your father&rsquo;s wishes and we can discuss his options with him at the initial appointment. It cannot be used until it is registered with the Office of the Public Guardian, and we would be happy to deal with this too.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Why not read our&nbsp;<a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/13_Factsheet - Lasting Power of Attorney.docx?1322579386" target="_blank">FREE GUIDE</a>&nbsp;to LPAs?</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold;">What do I do next?</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We are always keen to find the best solution possible for your particular circumstances, and we know that no two families are the same. Whatever your circumstances we will be able advise you as to the best way forward.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment with our expert Private Client department, call <span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span></strong>*<strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjones.co.uk">info@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>', '2011-01-21 13:08:20', '2015-06-24 10:19:44', '', '', 1, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>Making a Will is a good place to start when planning for your future</p>\r\n<p>Make a Will today</p>', 'wom with baby.JPG', 'image/pjpeg', 191221, '2011-03-01 12:21:06', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'LastingPowerOfAttorney.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 52253, '2011-01-21 13:10:35', 'Lasting Power of Attorney', '', '', 'Lasting Power of Attorney', '/page/making-a-will', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '/page/making-a-will', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(115, '<span class="family">Services for <span>you & your family</span></span>', 'services_for_you_and_your_family', 'Services for you & your family', 21, 0, 0, 0, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2>We''re with you every step of the way&hellip;</h2>\r\n<p>You may never know when you are going to need the services of a solicitor, but one thing is for sure, you will need one at some point if your life. Whatever the matter let us worry about the legal jargon; you just sit back and relax in the knowledge that your case is safe in our hands.</p>\r\n<p>At Banner Jones we are here to help and guide you through all of life&rsquo;s little challenges and we&rsquo;re committed to being with you every step of the way.</p>\r\n<p>Through the good times...</p>\r\n<ul class="bullet_black_button">\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/residential-property">Moving House?</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/pre-or-postmarital-partnership-agreements">Getting Married?</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/wills">Had a baby?</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>And the bad...</p>\r\n<ul class="bullet_black_button">\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/personal-injury">Had an accident?</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/probate">Lost a loved one?</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/divorce-and-separation">Relationship breaking down?</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Instructing a solicitor can often be a daunting task especially when you sometimes have no idea how much it will cost you. With the Banner Jones Fixed Fee promise you can be reassured that wherever possible you will know exactly what you are going to pay for your work upfront. Refreshing?</p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../page/about-us">Read more about us</a>.</p>', '2010-11-12 17:09:42', '2011-01-24 13:22:05', '', '', 2, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'Family.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 43061, '2011-01-11 11:46:57', 'Family', '', '', 'Family', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NU