(139, 'Road Traffic Accidents', 'road_traffic_accidents', 'Road Traffic Accident Claims | Personal Injury Chesterfield', 134, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<div id="c3061" class="csc">\r\n<div class="clear">\r\n<h2 class="subhead"><span class="alt">We are experts in</span>&nbsp;r<span>oad traffic accident claims.</span></h2>\r\n<p class="subhead">Car and road traffic accidents are one of the most common causes of personal injury. If you, or a family member, have obtained a road traffic accident injury, through no fault of your own; we can&nbsp;help you. Our&nbsp;team of specialist&nbsp;solicitors will be able to advise you on your<strong>&nbsp;</strong>claim whether you were on foot, in a car, or on a motorbike&nbsp;or bike.</p>\r\n<p class="subhead">For more information about the types of road traffic accidents covered and what you can do to get the ball rolling on your claim, check out our infographic below:</p>\r\n<p class="subhead"><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/107_Road Traffic.pdf?1418042070" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/107_Road Traffic.pdf?1418042070" target="_blank"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/139/contained_images/f2bbe231fe5b_377_Road Traffic Accidents.JPG?1418042304" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="250" /></a></p>\r\n<p class="standout_link" style="text-align: center;"><a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Road Traffic Accidents'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/107_Road Traffic.pdf?1418042070" target="_blank">Open Infographic</a></p>\r\n<p class="subhead">We can offer you help with simple bruising and whiplash claims, through to representation of more serious or even fatal accidents. We have over 45 years of experience in high value personal injury claims.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="c3060" class="csc">\r\n<div class="content">Our solicitors are experienced in assessing road traffic claims for accidents involving:</div>\r\n<div class="content">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Car drivers</li>\r\n<li>Passengers</li>\r\n<li>Cyclists</li>\r\n<li>Pedestrians</li>\r\n<li>Public Transport</li>\r\n<li>Motorcyclists</li>\r\n<li>Claims against the Motor Insurers Bureau (MIB)</li>\r\n<li>Overseas RTAs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>We can advise you on your injuries and any financial losses incurred. You will get a free, initial consultation on a no win, no fee basis.<br /><br />If you have been seriously injured in a road traffic accident, we do everything we can to ensure you have easy access to additional support and advice on issues such as employment, benefit and welfare rights. We can even do home visits if required.<br /><br />We can also consider whether interim payments of compensation may be available to relieve financial pressures, and cover immediate expenses.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Uninsured motorist</h2>\r\n<p>If your injuries were caused by the negligent driving of an uninsured motorist, your claim could be referred to the Motor Insurers Bureau under the &ldquo;Uninsured Drivers Agreement&rdquo;. MIB claims can be complex and it is important to instruct an experienced solicitor.</p>\r\n<h2>Untraced motorist</h2>\r\n<p>Even if the motorist failed to stop and you were unable to obtain the registration number of the vehicle, a claim can be pursued against the Motor Insurers Bureau under the &ldquo;Untraced Drivers Agreement&rdquo;.&nbsp; It is a condition, however, that the accident be reported to the Police within 5 days of the incident if claiming for property damage, or within 14 days if claiming for personal injuries. Failure to do so will jeopardise a claim.</p>\r\n<p>If you think you have a compensation claim, contact us now for a <strong>free assessment </strong>of your case. You can also drop in to our dedicated Accident Claims Centre on Glumangate in Chesterfield. No appointment is necessary. We are your local experts and pride ourselves on winning over 95% of the cases we take on.</p>\r\n<p><strong>You can also call us on&nbsp;<span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span>* or&nbsp;</strong><strong>email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:claims@bannerjones.co.uk">claims@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>\r\n<p><img src="../../../assets/page_contents/139/contained_images/a85502100a18_245_British Bike association.png?1391702877" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="225" height="129" /></p>\r\n</div>', '2011-05-09 14:40:56', '2015-03-19 11:35:19', 'If you''ve had a car or road traffic accident and want to claim the compensation you deserve, contact us today for your free, initial consultation.', '', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>We can help</p>\r\n<p>Call now 0333 200 2311</p>', '180_new PI team mar 13.JPG', 'image/jpeg', 214936, '2013-03-28 10:16:10', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'RoadTrafficAccidents.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 28269, '2011-05-20 10:44:56', 'Road Traffic Accidents', '', '', 'Road Traffic Accidents', '', '', 2, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '<img src="../../../assets/stored_images/original/377_Road Traffic Accidents.JPG?1418042304" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="250" />\r\n<div><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong><a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Road Traffic Accidents'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/107_Road Traffic.pdf?1418042070" target="_blank">Road Traffic Accidents</a></strong></span></div>', 'Road Traffic Accident Claims', ''),
(140, 'Slips and Trips', 'slips_and_trips', 'Slip Injury Compensation Claims | Personal Injury', 135, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<div id="pane1" class="tabPaneOn">\r\n<div class="cmsContent">\r\n<h2>We''re with you every step of the way</h2>\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;ve fallen and been injured, we can advise as to whether you might have&nbsp;a slip injury claim. We&rsquo;ve successfully helped people recover compensation after slips in supermarkets, restaurants, shops, pubs and many other locations.</p>\r\n<p>If you''ve fallen and you''re considering making a claim for compensation, check out our infographic below that details your options and our approach to your claim.</p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/108_Slips and Trips.pdf?1418042106" target="_blank"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/140/contained_images/26120f03e697_378_Slips and Trips.JPG?1418042313" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="250" /></a></p>\r\n<p class="standout_link" style="text-align: center;"><a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Slips &amp; Trips'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/108_Slips and Trips.pdf?1418042106" target="_blank">Open Infographic</a></p>\r\n<p>The owners or occupiers of public or commercial premises have a duty of care to ensure your safety. If your accident happened on their premises, and we can prove they failed in that duty, we should be able to make a strong case for a slip injury compensation claim.</p>\r\n<p>Our team&nbsp;specialise in accident claims involving slipping/tripping injuries. If you have a right to pursue a claim, we&rsquo;ll do everything we can to help you get the compensation you deserve.</p>\r\n<p>Not only that, but if your slip injuries are such that you&rsquo;re incapacitated, they&rsquo;ll ensure you get the right rehabilitation support to help you get back on an even keel. We can also do home visits during the process if required.</p>\r\n<p>If you slipped in a shop, pub or other public place, try and take photos of the area where you slipped. This will help us to prove that someone else was at fault for your accident. You should also make sure that your slip is recorded in the accident book, if applicable. It is also useful to collect the names and addresses of any witnesses who can help to piece together what happened.</p>\r\n<h2>Accidents in Public Places</h2>\r\n<p>Every year in the UK, thousands of people are injured due to an accident in a public place. Most recover from their injuries with time but the knock-on effect for others can mean long term disability, ongoing pain and continuing financial losses. If you have been injured as a result of an accident in a public place, such as a trip, slip or fall, then you could be entitled to make an accident claim to compensate you for your injuries.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Thousands of people every year experience some form of accident in a public place for which they could make an accident compensation claim. This could be the result of a trip, slip, fall or being struck by falling objects.</p>\r\n<p>The responsibility for the accident will often lie with the owner of the premises or property in which the accident took place, or the local authority responsible for maintaining public spaces. They have a legal responsibility known as a "duty of care" to minimise the risk of accidents, and where we can prove you were injured because that duty was breached, we&rsquo;ll pursue an accident compensation claim on your behalf.</p>\r\n<p>Why not drop into our dedicated Accident Claim Centre on Glumangate in Chesterfield? It''s no appointment necessary, and you''ll see an expert, not just a claims manager.</p>\r\n<p><strong>If you think you might have a compensation claim, contact our expert Personal Injury solicitors&nbsp;<strong>for a no obligation chat&nbsp;</strong>on <span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span>*,&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:claims@bannerjones.co.uk">claims@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '2011-05-09 15:04:28', '2015-03-19 11:35:30', 'If you''ve slipped and suffered an injury, contact us for your free consultation to claim the compensation you deserve. We have a 95% success rate!', '', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>Call us now on 0333 200 2311</p>\r\n<p>or click here to email <a href="mailto:claim@bannerjones.co.uk">claim@bannerjones.co.uk</a></p>', '180_new PI team mar 13.JPG', 'image/jpeg', 214936, '2013-03-28 10:17:11', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'SlipsAndTrips.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 29372, '2011-05-20 10:43:11', 'Slips and Trips', '', '', 'Slips and Trips', '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '<img src="../../../assets/stored_images/original/378_Slips and Trips.JPG?1418042313" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="250" />\r\n<div><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Slips &amp; Trips'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/108_Slips and Trips.pdf?1418042106" target="_blank">Slips and Trips</a></span></strong></div>', 'Slips and Trips', ''),
(141, 'Accidents at Work', 'accidents_at_work', 'Workplace Accident Compensation Claims | Personal Injury', 136, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<div id="c3581" class="csc">\r\n<div class="content">\r\n<p class="teaser">The HSE has stated that are 150,000 non-fatal injuries being reported each year whilst, sadly, 200 people lose their lives due to an accident or injury at work. In addition, it is estimated that 2 million people suffer from ill health caused or exacerbated by accidents and injury at work. Whilst some of these injuries are minor, some have more serious consequences, such as time off work, financial and emotional strain or even permanent disability.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="teaser">Whatever your circumstances, we''ll be with you every step of the way. We can even arrange home visits to your during this process, if required.</p>\r\n<p class="teaser">Take a look at our infographic below that walks you through your options if you''ve had an accident at work:</p>\r\n<p class="teaser"><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/110_AccidentsAtWork.pdf?1418381839" target="_blank"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/141/contained_images/fca975dcc9d0_383_accidents at work snippet.JPG?1418382751" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="250" /></a></p>\r\n<p class="standout_link" style="text-align: center;"><a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Accidents At Work'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/110_AccidentsAtWork.pdf?1418381839" target="_blank">Open Infographic</a></p>\r\n<p class="teaser">Compensation can go a long way to ease the burden that an accident or injury at work has caused, and choosing the right solicitor for your case is one of the most important decisions you&rsquo;ll have to make.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="teaser">Our expert team of solicitors has over 45 years of experience with high value personal injury claims, meaning you''ll speak to an expert and not just a claims manager.</p>\r\n<p class="teaser">There are many types of accident and injury suffered at work that you may be able to claim compensation for. Below are just a selection of the ones our team&nbsp;of injury solicitors will be able to help with:</p>\r\n<strong> \r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Accidents on Building/Construction sites</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Mesothelioma Claims and other Asbestos related diseases</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Loss of hearing</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Hand Arm Vibration Syndrome</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Skin conditions</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Severe injuries resulting in amputation</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</strong> \r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Why not drop in to our dedicated Accident Claim Centre on Glumangate in Chesterfield? You''ll get a free, initial consultation and it''s no appointment necessary. Additionally, we work on a no win, no fee basis.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Alternatively, to see whether you have a claim, contact our expert Personal Injury solicitors for a no obligation chat on <span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span>*,&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:claims@bannerjones.co.uk">claims@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '2011-05-09 15:31:15', '2015-03-19 11:35:39', 'If you''ve had an accident at work and sustained an injury, you could claim compensation. Contact us today for your free, no obligation chat. No win, no fee.', '', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>We can help you</p>\r\n<p>0333 200 2311</p>\r\n<p>Free no obligation advice</p>', '4_AccreditedPersonalInjury.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 31123, '2011-05-13 13:22:01', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'AccidentsAtWork.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 34262, '2011-05-20 10:42:54', 'Accidents at Work', '', '', 'Accidents at Work', '', '', 2, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '<img src="../../../assets/stored_images/original/383_accidents at work snippet.JPG?1418382751" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="250" />\r\n<div><br />\r\n<div><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Accidents At Work'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/110_AccidentsAtWork.pdf?1418381839" target="_blank">Accidents At Work</a></span></strong></div>\r\n</div>', 'Accidents at Work', ''),
(142, 'Work Related Illness', 'work_related_illness', 'Work Related Illness | No Win, No Fee Personal Injury Claims', 137, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p>Employers have a responsibility to protect their employees from work related accidents and illnesses.</p>\r\n<p>When this protection is missing or flawed, serious personal injury or even death can result and you may be entitled to a compensation claim. If you''re seriously ill, we can even offer home visits to you during this process, if required.</p>\r\n<p>Take a look at our infographic below that explains your options, should you have acquired a work related illness:</p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/113_WorkRelatedIllness.pdf?1418382248" target="_blank"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/142/contained_images/bfff53c3f112_387_work related illness snippet.JPG?1418382795" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="250" /></a></p>\r\n<p class="standout_link" style="text-align: center;"><a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Work Related Illness'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/113_WorkRelatedIllness.pdf?1418382248" target="_blank">Open Infographic</a></p>\r\n<p>Some of the more common work related illnesses include:</p>\r\n<span style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold;"> \r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Asbestos related diseases</li>\r\n<li>Carpal tunnel syndrome</li>\r\n<li>Acoustic shock/hearing loss</li>\r\n<li>Vibration white finger</li>\r\n<li>Repetitive strain</li>\r\n<li>Occupational asthma</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</span> \r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Our specialist team of personal injury solicitors have over 45 years of experience with high value personal injury claims, so you''ll be speaking to an expert and not just a claims manager.</p>\r\n<p>Why not drop in to our dedicated Accident Claim Centre on Glumangate in Chesterfield? You''ll get a free, initial consultation and it''s no appointment necessary. We also work on a no win, no fee basis, so you''ve got nothing to lose.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Alternatively, if you think you have a claim, contact our expert Personal Injury solicitors for a no obligation chat on <span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span>*,&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:claims@bannerjones.co.uk">claims@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>', '2011-05-09 15:48:08', '2015-03-19 11:35:49', 'If you''ve suffered a work related illness, contact us today for your free consultation to get the compensation you deserve. No win, no fee!', '', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>Free Initial Advice</p>\r\n<p>0333 200 2311</p>\r\n<p>Excellent success rate</p>', '4_AccreditedPersonalInjury.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 31123, '2011-05-13 13:50:14', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'WorkRelatedIllness.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 35678, '2011-05-20 10:45:00', 'Work Related Illness', '', '', 'Work Related Illness', '', '', 2, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '<img src="../../../assets/stored_images/original/387_work related illness snippet.JPG?1418382795" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="250" />\r\n<div><br />\r\n<div><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Work Related Illness'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/113_WorkRelatedIllness.pdf?1418382248" target="_blank">Work Related Illness</a></span></strong></div>\r\n</div>', '', '');
