(199, ' Assessment Information Meeting', '_assessment_information_meeting', 'Free Initial Assessment Meeting | Family Law Solicitors in Sheffield | Banner Jones', 189, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2>FREE Assessment Information Meeting - AIM</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We understand that when relationships break down it is often very hard to know which way to&nbsp;turn. To help you, we have launched a new scheme called an AIM which will take you through what your options are.&nbsp; The Assessment Information Meetings are free and can be done over the phone or in person, whatever suits you.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">In the free no obligation meeting we will talk you through what your options are so that you have a clear understanding of how you could proceed.&nbsp; <strong>Please note the free AIM meeting only applies to our Family Law department.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We offer a full spectrum of family law services from our offices in Chesterfield, Mansfield and Sheffield, so we will always have the right solution for your needs.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We can offer:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Free Mediation on all Family issues *subject to eligibility</li>\r\n<li>Discounted advice if Legal Aid is not applicable ''Family Assist''</li>\r\n<li>''Pay as you go'' fixed fee advice</li>\r\n<li>Fixed Fee Divorce solutions</li>\r\n<li>Fixed Fee family Court representation</li>\r\n<li>Proactive tailored advice and representation</li>\r\n<li>Fixed Fee document checking &amp; preparation service</li>\r\n<li>Fixed Fee mediation with Midlands Mediation</li>\r\n<li>Collaborative law</li>\r\n<li>''Next step'' planning</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>We have&nbsp;offices in Chesterfield, Sheffield, Dronfield, Mansfield, Nottingham, Derby, Ilkeston and Bulwell.<br /><br /><strong><span style="color: #333333;">To book your FREE AIM,</span>&nbsp;or to arrange an appointment with our expert Family Law department, call <span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span>*&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjones.co.uk">info@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>', '2013-12-17 11:17:14', '2015-07-22 09:35:04', 'We offer a free assessment information meeting (AIM) for family cases to go through your options with no obligations. Get in touch to find out more.', '', 2, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0, 'Book Your FREE AIM today', 'AIM_LOGO.jpg', 'image/pjpeg', 70392, '2013-12-17 11:41:21', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', 'Assessment Information Meeting', '<div itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Review-aggregate">\r\n    <span itemprop="itemreviewed">Banner Jones Family Law Reviews</span>    \r\n    <span itemprop="rating" itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Rating">\r\n      <span itemprop="average">4.5</span>\r\n      out of <span itemprop="best">5</span>\r\n    </span>\r\n    based on <span itemprop="votes">6</span> ratings.    \r\n</div>'),
