(208, 'Savings and Investments', 'savings_and_investments', 'Savings and Investments', 198, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p style="text-align: justify;">Saving for your future and accumulating your wealth is one of the toughest challenges you will face. It requires hard work, determination and discipline but most importantly of all it requires careful planning. It is important to first understand your circumstances, be realistic with timescales and to carefully consider your attitude towards risk and loss. From this we can give you the advice, the ideas and the plan to increase your wealth and improve your financial security.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Deciding where best to invest and save your money need not be challenging. We can help clients with cash on deposit to achieve the returns they are looking for. We can do this by researching the market for you and providing recommendations and solutions that match your objectives. We don&rsquo;t only look on an absolute return basis; we also consider the most tax efficient methods available and your risk tolerance parameters.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Don&rsquo;t worry; we will work with you closely in order to fully understand your financial planning needs and carefully consider your attitude towards risk.</li>\r\n<li>Using our diverse knowledge of investments and a variety of research tools we can make sound financial recommendations that meet your objectives.</li>\r\n<li>We avoid any jargon where possible so that you fully understand how and where your money is invested.</li>\r\n<li>We will review your portfolio for you on a regular basis to help take the stress out of investing</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, call 01246 560570</strong><strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk">info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>Banner Jones Wealth Management&nbsp; is:</em></p>\r\n<p><em>-&nbsp;the trading name of Banner Jones Wealth Management LLP </em><em>(registered in England &amp; Wales, number OC380075)</em></p>\r\n<p><em>-a separate&nbsp;legal entity&nbsp;to Banner&nbsp;Jones ltd</em></p>\r\n<p><em>-is not a law firm&nbsp;authorised or regulated by the Solicitors Regulation Authority</em></p>\r\n<p><em>-an&nbsp;&nbsp;Appointed Representative of Future Life Wealth Management Ltd which is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.</em></p>', '2014-01-03 10:45:16', '2015-03-06 16:06:00', '', '', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, 'Your Wealth in Good Hands', '83_iStock_000007854419XSmall.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 99712, '2014-01-03 10:47:34', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(209, 'Pensions', 'pensions', 'Pensions', 199, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Retirement &amp; Pensions</strong></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Planning and saving for our retirement is becoming one of the biggest challenges of modern life, with life expectancy increasing and state pension provisions dwindling. It is becoming apparent that the majority of us will require a significant nest egg in order to live comfortably in retirement. <br />Having said all of this, many of us still do not contribute enough into our pensions or in some extreme circumstances nothing at all!&nbsp;&nbsp;We can help.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Even those with pensions often do not really understand the&nbsp;mecahnics and they certainly don''t realise just how much it can be costing to have their pension managed each year.&nbsp; Let us help you uncover some of the mystery and set you on the right path.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style="text-align: left;">\r\n<li>If planned for effectively, retirement can feel like the longest holiday of your life, however if you don&rsquo;t&nbsp; it can quickly feel like your longest period of unemployment.</li>\r\n<li>We can help you prepare for your retirement whether you are in your early twenties or late fifties.</li>\r\n<li>We shall work closely with you to understand your post-retirement goals.</li>\r\n<li>We can offer retirement solutions specific to the age you wish to retire and the flexibility of income you will require.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><br />With so much to consider we can assess your options and help you make the right decisions.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, call 01246 560570</strong><strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk">info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>Banner Jones Wealth Management&nbsp; is:</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-&nbsp;the trading name of Banner Jones Wealth Management LLP </em><em>(registered in England &amp; Wales, number OC380075)</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-a separate&nbsp;legal entity&nbsp;to Banner&nbsp;Jones ltd</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-is not a law firm&nbsp;authorised or regulated by the Solicitors Regulation Authority</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-an&nbsp;&nbsp;Appointed Representative of Future Life Wealth Management Ltd which is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.</em></p>', '2014-01-03 10:49:05', '2015-03-06 16:07:42', '', '', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(210, 'Holistic Financial Planning', 'holistic_financial_planning', 'Holistic Financial Planning', 200, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p style="text-align: justify;">For professionals and business owners alike, it is beneficial to assess whether your financial strategy is likely to meet with your personal aims and objectives and provide you with your desired lifestyle in retirement.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We offer a comprehensive financial plan; this includes a valuable lifetime cash flow forecast, an indication as to whether their financial strategy will enable you to achieve your personal lifestyle goals and leave you with a financially secure life, or whether they are likely to run out of capital at some point. We can also build scenarios, test the ''what if'' scenarios which&nbsp;invariably arise, such as death of a partner, or enforced retirement due to illness or disability.&nbsp;&nbsp; <br /><br />How powerful would it be for you to know when you could afford to retire, or calculate the sums you need to realise from the sale of the business in order to achieve and/or maintain the desired lifestyle in retirement?</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Contact us today to plan for your future</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, call 01246 560570</strong><strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk">info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>Banner Jones Wealth Management&nbsp; is:</em></p>\r\n<p><em>-&nbsp;the trading name of Banner Jones Wealth Management LLP </em><em>(registered in England &amp; Wales, number OC380075)</em></p>\r\n<p><em>-a separate&nbsp;legal entity&nbsp;to Banner&nbsp;Jones ltd</em></p>\r\n<p><em>-is not a law firm&nbsp;authorised or regulated by the Solicitors Regulation Authority</em></p>\r\n<p><em>-an&nbsp;&nbsp;Appointed Representative of Future Life Wealth Management Ltd which is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>', '2014-01-03 10:57:51', '2015-03-06 16:08:36', '', '', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(211, ' Releasing Equity', '_releasing_equity', ' Releasing Equity', 201, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p style="text-align: left;">We are all living longer which means that we may need to consider alternative ways to fund our retirement.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Equity Release is an option where you can continue to live in your house, using the equity that is tied up in your home to provide you with a lump sum<strong>. </strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Talk to us today to see how we can help you release the equity in your home.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, call 01246 560570</strong><strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk">info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk</a>.</strong></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>Banner Jones Wealth Management&nbsp; is:</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-&nbsp;the trading name of Banner Jones Wealth Management LLP </em><em>(registered in England &amp; Wales, number OC380075)</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-a separate&nbsp;legal entity&nbsp;to Banner&nbsp;Jones ltd</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-is not a law firm&nbsp;authorised or regulated by the Solicitors Regulation Authority</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-an&nbsp;&nbsp;Appointed Representative of Future Life Wealth Management Ltd which is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.</em></p>', '2014-01-03 11:02:04', '2015-03-06 16:09:12', '', '', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, 'Equity Release could be the answer', '69_iStock_000003465599XSmall.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 245782, '2014-01-03 11:05:02', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', '');
