(212, 'Long Term Care Planning', 'long_term_care_planning', 'Long Term Care Planning', 202, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p style="text-align: left;">As we grow older and require more care, we are entering one of the most emotional and daunting period of our lives. Despite this, very few people seek professional advice on what is probably one of the largest financial commitments they have ever made - paying for care home fees. Whether you are being funded by the State or paying privately for your care, there is much to consider. Choosing the right type of care requires considerable research and consideration and we can help you make the right decision based on your circumstances.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We will discuss with you any concerns you have regarding long term care and help put you in the strongest position to make decisions on your future.&nbsp; We will help you understand care fees and the affect they have on your assets and finances.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We will also help to guide you through the maze of legislation and benefits so that you are in the best place to make the right decisions.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, call 01246 560570</strong><strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk">info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>Banner Jones Wealth Management&nbsp; is:</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-&nbsp;the trading name of Banner Jones Wealth Management LLP </em><em>(registered in England &amp; Wales, number OC380075)</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-a separate&nbsp;legal entity&nbsp;to Banner&nbsp;Jones ltd</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-is not a law firm&nbsp;authorised or regulated by the Solicitors Regulation Authority</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-an&nbsp;&nbsp;Appointed Representative of Future Life Wealth Management Ltd which is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority</em></p>', '2014-01-03 11:06:46', '2015-03-06 16:09:33', '', '', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, 'We can help', '106_iStock_000013194966XSmall.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 163791, '2014-01-03 11:09:06', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(213, 'Inheritance and Estate Planning', 'inheritance_and_estate_planning', 'Inheritance and Estate Planning', 203, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2 style="text-align: left;">Inheritance Tax Planning</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Much can be achieved by careful planning and drafting of Wills, and the ability to transfer the unused portion of a nil rate band between spouses or civil partners. This has greatly improved the Inheritance Tax position for many people. However, for those with larger estates, alternative planning solutions are still required and we are experienced in advising on some less widely known opportunities to reduce the impact of IHT.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We will assess how we can minimise your tax liability whilst maximising what you are able to pass on to your loved ones.</p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Estate Protection</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We see<strong> </strong>Life Assurance as a last resort, but its use in conjunction with the right Trust arrangements can be a powerful planning tool in preserving hard-earned assets for the next generation for a fraction of the cost of the IHT bill. We have access to many years&rsquo; experience in advising on the most suitable type of policies to provide you with the reassurance that the provisions&nbsp;you take out will perform the task that youwant it to.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold;">Advice to Trustees</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">The Trustee Act 2000 imposes specific duties on Trustees. These include the implementation of a standard investment criteria, regular revision of the suitability of the chosen investment strategy, and commensurately, estate planning requires the need for diversification through differing types of investments held. We offer access to advice to Trustees on the suitability of different asset classes and investment risk as well as on the most tax-efficient investment products, to meet the Trust&rsquo;s objectives.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, call 01246 560570</strong><strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk">info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>Banner Jones Wealth Management&nbsp; is:</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-&nbsp;the trading name of Banner Jones Wealth Management LLP </em><em>(registered in England &amp; Wales, number OC380075)</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-a separate&nbsp;legal entity&nbsp;to Banner&nbsp;Jones ltd</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-is not a law firm&nbsp;authorised or regulated by the Solicitors Regulation Authority</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-an&nbsp;&nbsp;Appointed Representative of Future Life Wealth Management Ltd which is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority</em></p>', '2014-01-03 11:11:32', '2015-03-06 16:10:17', '', '', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(214, 'Insurance and Protection', 'insurance_and_protection', 'Insurance and Protection', 204, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p style="text-align: left;">It is important&nbsp;to realise that everyone faces risks in their future and that safeguarding the financial security of your family and dependents is essential.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">With this in mind,&nbsp;you may &nbsp;want to make provisions to protect your families from financial liabilities in the unfortunate event of death, critical illness or unemployment.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We have extensive experience of reviewing and establishing protection arrangements to cover an array of eventualities. Our advisers, researchers and administrators regularly review and implement all types of insurance and protection.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Due to the fact that we are completely independent, we are able to review protection products across the whole of the market place. We can therefore provide an impartial service which is bespoke and uniquely tailored towards your individual requirements and circumstances.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, call 01246 560570</strong><strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk">info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>Banner Jones Wealth Management&nbsp; is:</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-&nbsp;the trading name of Banner Jones Wealth Management LLP </em><em>(registered in England &amp; Wales, number OC380075)</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-a separate&nbsp;legal entity&nbsp;to Banner&nbsp;Jones ltd</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-is not a law firm&nbsp;authorised or regulated by the Solicitors Regulation Authority</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-an&nbsp;&nbsp;Appointed Representative of Future Life Wealth Management Ltd which is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority</em></p>', '2014-01-03 11:18:35', '2015-03-06 16:10:33', '', '', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(215, 'Matrimonial and Divorce', 'matrimonial_and_divorce', 'Matrimonial and Divorce', 205, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p style="text-align: left;">Divorce can be an incredibly difficult and stressful time for all involved. We will work closely with you, your family and your trusted lawyers to ensure you reach the best possible outcome.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Divorce &amp; Pensions</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">When a marriage or civil partnership breaks down, a pension fund is often one of the major components of the financial settlement. It is important that the treatment of the pension fund is given careful thought and consideration. Our access to impartial advice will help provide a comprehensive overview, including a transfer value analysis if necessary, culminating in a report on the options available, including offset, earmarking and pension sharing orders.<br /><br />Where a pension sharing order is awarded we provide access to all the necessary impartial advice, assessing a suitable future investment strategy and administrative support to complete the transaction to a personal pension arrangement.</p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Protection</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">The death, serious illness or loss of employment of a divorced spouse and/or parent can have disastrous financial consequences for dependents who have been awarded earmarking orders. Serious consideration should be given to protecting term maintenance payments, or at the very least these issues discussed and offered to every client at risk.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, call 01246 560570</strong><strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk">info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>Banner Jones Wealth Management&nbsp; is:</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-&nbsp;the trading name of Banner Jones Wealth Management LLP </em><em>(registered in England &amp; Wales, number OC380075)</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-a separate&nbsp;legal entity&nbsp;to Banner&nbsp;Jones ltd</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-is not a law firm&nbsp;authorised or regulated by the Solicitors Regulation Authority</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-an&nbsp;&nbsp;Appointed Representative of Future Life Wealth Management Ltd which is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority</em></p>', '2014-01-03 11:22:22', '2015-03-06 16:11:06', '', '', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, 'Helping you maximise your financial settlement', '158_woman and child.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 274596, '2014-01-03 11:25:03', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(216, 'School Fees Planning', 'school_fees_planning', 'School Fees Planning', 206, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p style="text-align: left;">School fee planning is a niche area of advice that we offer at Banner Jones Wealth Management, however it&nbsp;is incredibly sought after.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Those that send children to private school realise the significance of covering these costs in the most efficient way. They can become a huge burden without proper advice, if they are not properly planned and managed.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Here are the top three questions parents ask about private school fees:-</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Can we afford it? (Average school fees are now approx. &pound;300,000*)</li>\r\n<li>Is there a more efficient way to pay?</li>\r\n<li>What impact will school fees have on our lifestyle?</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Without definitively answering these questions school fees could seriously damage your wealth!<br />The Telegraph reported that 4 in 10 parents fear that they could run out of money before their children&rsquo;s&rsquo; education is complete**</p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Why is this important?</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We like to think of school fees planning like architecture. Without an Architect and a good design plan a building may be ugly and inefficient, it may even collapse altogether. In the same way, without a school fees plan you will probably lose out on substantial benefits and efficiencies and at worst your life could end up in financial turmoil.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">What&rsquo;s in it for me?</span><br />1. Make school fees more affordable<br />2. Protect against life&rsquo;s big pitfalls<br />3. Improve cost and tax efficiencies<br />4. Build school fees into your overall financial life plan<br />5. Manage cash flow<br />6. Peace of mind</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">In reality our clients often save thousands, improve their long-term lifestyles and often significantly reduce their tax liabilities! If any of these would appeal to you, get in touch today.</p>\r\n<p class="ecxmsonormal" style="text-align: left;">* Based on the Independent School Council Census 2013, a 4 year old child going into Reception in Autumn 2013 would incur the following fees throughout his/her education, allowing for the 3.9% annual inflation rate from 2012 - 13 (the lowest since 1994).&nbsp;We have taken the average fees by category for this year applying the annual inflation rate for 2012/13 from the Census.</p>\r\n<p class="ecxmsonormal" style="text-align: left;">Primary School (4 &ndash; 10) - &pound;76,965</p>\r\n<p class="ecxmsonormal" style="text-align: left;">Secondary School (11 - 15) - &pound;111,834</p>\r\n<p class="ecxmsonormal" style="text-align: left;">Sixth Form College (16 &ndash; 17) - &pound;61,650</p>\r\n<p class="ecxmsonormal" style="text-align: left;">University Tuition Fees (18 &ndash; 21) - &pound;46,152</p>\r\n<p class="ecxmsonormal" style="text-align: left;">Total - &pound;296,601</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">**http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/personalfinance/savings/2820204/School-fee-plans-face-toughest-test.html</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, call 01246 560570</strong><strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk">info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>Banner Jones Wealth Management&nbsp; is:</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-&nbsp;the trading name of Banner Jones Wealth Management LLP </em><em>(registered in England &amp; Wales, number OC380075)</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-a separate&nbsp;legal entity&nbsp;to Banner&nbsp;Jones ltd</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-is not a law firm&nbsp;authorised or regulated by the Solicitors Regulation Authority</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>-an&nbsp;&nbsp;Appointed Representative of Future Life Wealth Management Ltd which is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority</em></p>', '2014-01-03 11:40:24', '2015-03-06 16:12:15', '', '', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>Managing School Fees</p>\r\n<p>We can help</p>', '164_teachers.JPG', 'image/jpeg', 223703, '2014-01-03 11:44:17', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(217, 'Auto-Enrolment', 'autoenrolment', 'Auto-Enrolment', 207, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2><strong>Automatic enrolment &ndash; Is your business ready for the challenge?</strong></h2>\r\n<p><strong><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The Government estimates that millions of people in the UK are currently not saving enough for their retirement. To help solve this problem, the Government has introduced legislation that means every employer will have a duty to put a pension scheme in place. You&rsquo;ll also have to automatically enrol certain workers into the scheme and make contributions on their behalf.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">This presents a huge challenge for your business. You&rsquo;ll need to understand your automatic enrolment duties, the impact on your business and the changes you&rsquo;ll have to make.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We can help you with this challenge. We offer a range of services, in conjunction with Banner Jones Wealth Management LLP, which will help you to understand and prepare for automatic enrolment. By starting to plan now, we can help you to mitigate the costs and minimise the disruption to your business.</p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><br /></span></strong>What does it mean for you?</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Don&rsquo;t under-estimate what&rsquo;s involved.&nbsp;<strong>This process may take longer than you think. You need to have formulated your plan at least 12 months before your staging date.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">There&rsquo;s a lot for you to think about. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<li>Does your current pension arrangement qualify as an automatic enrolment scheme?</li>\r\n<li>How will you communicate with your workers and ensure you get the right message across?</li>\r\n<li>Have you considered the additional administration and cost involved in meeting the new requirements?</li>\r\n<li>Will your existing payroll process need to be altered?</li>\r\n<li>Will you be able to cope with the additional administration burden?</li>\r\n<li>Will you be able to put new processes in place and comply with record keeping and reporting requirements in time?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">How we can help</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We will provide you with practical help and advice every step of the way through automatic enrolment.</p>\r\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<li>We can identify your staging date. This is the date your employer duties will start. </li>\r\n<li>We can review any pension schemes you have in place to find out what you have to do to make it suitable for automatic enrolment.</li>\r\n<li>We can review your workforce to help you understand what your new duties will be.</li>\r\n<li>We can design and implement the right pension scheme for your business and your workers.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>The next steps</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">If you fail to automatically enrol your workers into a pension scheme by your staging date you could face fines of up to &pound;10,000 per day.&nbsp; Act now to make sure this doesn&rsquo;t happen to you.<br /><br /><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment to confirm your staging date, call 01246 560570</strong><strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk">info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>Banner Jones Wealth Management&nbsp; is:</em></p>\r\n<p><em>-&nbsp;the trading name of Banner Jones Wealth Management LLP </em><em>(registered in England &amp; Wales, number OC380075)</em></p>\r\n<p><em>-a separate&nbsp;legal entity&nbsp;to Banner&nbsp;Jones ltd</em></p>\r\n<p><em>-is not a law firm&nbsp;authorised or regulated by the Solicitors Regulation Authority</em></p>\r\n<p><em>-an&nbsp;&nbsp;Appointed Representative of Future Life Wealth Management Ltd which is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority</em></p>', '2014-01-03 11:48:05', '2015-03-06 15:59:41', '', '', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>When does your business need to enrol?</p>\r\n<p>We can help</p>', '108_iStock_000013859617XSmall.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 98164, '2014-01-03 11:59:44', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(218, 'Employee Benefits', 'employee_benefits', 'Employee Benefits', 208, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We can help you assess the different employee benefits that are available and which may be best suited to your business.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, call 01246 560570</strong><strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk">info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>Banner Jones Wealth Management&nbsp; is:</em></p>\r\n<p><em>-&nbsp;the trading name of Banner Jones Wealth Management LLP </em><em>(registered in England &amp; Wales, number OC380075)</em></p>\r\n<p><em>-a separate&nbsp;legal entity&nbsp;to Banner&nbsp;Jones ltd</em></p>\r\n<p><em>-is not a law firm&nbsp;authorised or regulated by the Solicitors Regulation Authority</em></p>\r\n<p><em>-an&nbsp;&nbsp;Appointed Representative of Future Life Wealth Management Ltd which is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority</em></p>', '2014-01-03 12:01:00', '2015-03-06 16:00:06', '', '', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(219, 'Business Protection', 'business_protection', 'Business Protection', 209, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2>Shareholder &amp; Key Man Insurance</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Why do business owners insure the desk they sit behind, but not the Key Person, the income generator sat behind it? It is fact that the vast majority of businesses in the UK do not have adequate protection for their most valuable assets, that is, their Key Personnel.&nbsp;&nbsp; As a business owner it is important you protect your most valuable assets, those key members of staff that generate your income. <br /><strong><br /></strong>What would you do if you lost your top salesman or administrator? <br />Could you cope without those other members of staff upon which your revenue relies?</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We have access to considerable experience in advising business owners on Key Man Protection and Partnership/Shareholder Protection. Where necessary we can assist with draft wordings of Cross/Double Option Agreements and business trust documentation to mitigate the effects of CGT and IHT.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><br />It is important to safeguard your income &amp; insure those employees so that you can continue operationally until replacements or other solutions are found.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment, call 01246 560570</strong><strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk">info@bannerjoneswm.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>Banner Jones Wealth Management&nbsp; is:</em></p>\r\n<p><em>-&nbsp;the trading name of Banner Jones Wealth Management LLP </em><em>(registered in England &amp; Wales, number OC380075)</em></p>\r\n<p><em>-a separate&nbsp;legal entity&nbsp;to Banner&nbsp;Jones ltd</em></p>\r\n<p><em>-is not a law firm&nbsp;authorised or regulated by the Solicitors Regulation Authority</em></p>\r\n<p><em>-an&nbsp;&nbsp;Appointed Representative of Future Life Wealth Management Ltd which is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority</em></p>\r\n<p class="clear">&nbsp;</p>', '2014-01-03 12:03:08', '2015-03-06 16:00:37', '', '', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>Key Man Insurance</p>\r\n<p>We can help</p>', '77_iStock_000005896679XSmall.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 115487, '2014-01-03 12:06:45', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', '', ''),
(220, 'Family', 'family', ' Family Law Solicitors in Sheffield & Chesterfield | Banner Jones ', 48, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2>At Banner Jones we are expert Family Law Solicitors</h2>\r\n<p>We understand that you may be going through a difficult time at the moment and, with that in mind, the Banner Jones Family Law team is here to help you. Our family solicitors in Sheffield, Chesterfield and all our offices provide specialist advice and guidance you need to help you and your family sort things out.</p>\r\n<p>The first thing we will do is talk you through all of your options as there may be several different routes you could take. Your advisor will explain all of your options in plain English, and make sure you understand how your case might progress. Our team pride themselves on providing the support and sensitivity you need throughout your family law case, but be assured - we will also take a strong and robust position when necessary.</p>\r\n<p>At Banner Jones Solicitors we have three specialist teams within our Family Law department providing expert advice in:</p>\r\n<p><strong><span><a href="../../../page/mediation" target="_blank">Mediation</a>&nbsp;</span></strong>- including specialist family mediators qualified in direct child consultation.</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="../../../page/care-proceedings" target="_blank">Care</a></span></strong>&nbsp;- including care proceedings and adoption orders.</p>\r\n<p><strong><span><a href="../../../page/relationships-and-children" target="_blank">Relationship and Children disputes</a></span></strong>&nbsp;- including divorce &amp; separation.</p>\r\n<p>We have&nbsp;offices in Sheffield, Chesterfield, Dronfield, Mansfield, Nottingham, Derby, Ilkeston and Bulwell.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment with our expert Family Law department, call <span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span></strong>*<strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjones.co.uk">info@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;"><strong><span style="text-align: center;">Divorce Across The Years</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p>Using recent data from the ONS, we''ve created this informative infographic about how divorce has changed over the years - from 1931 to today! Click below to learn more.</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/220/contained_images/390a2a10af84_405_divorce-snippet.JPG?1424864929" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="250" /></p>\r\n<p class="standout_link" style="text-align: center;"><a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Divorce Across the Years'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/118_DivorceInfographicV3.pdf?1424864905" target="_blank">&nbsp;Open Infographic</a></p>\r\n<p class="standout_link" style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="standout_link" style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>', '2010-11-15 10:33:52', '2015-07-22 08:25:01', 'We offer expert advice on family law, we also have a team of specialist family law solicitors who can offer guidance and support.', '', 1, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<strong>Our Family team have been ranked in the Legal 500 for their outstanding work</strong>', '359_UK_leading_firm_2014.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 7199, '2015-01-05 09:30:33', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'Family.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 41531, '2011-01-18 17:10:22', 'Family', '', '', 'Family', '/team_members', '', 6, 'family_highlight', '', '/team_members', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/67_Banner Jones Divorce Infographic V5 FINAL.pdf?1400500109" target="_blank">Download Divorce and Separation Infographic</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/67_Banner Jones Divorce Infographic V5 FINAL.pdf?1400500109" target="_blank"><img src="../../../assets/stored_images/original/262_Divorce.png?1397224179" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Planning for Your Future'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/56_Family - A4 planning for your future.pdf?1391598392" target="_blank">Download Planning for Your Future Guide</a></p>\r\n<p><img src="../../../assets/stored_images/original/243_Future.png?1390499805" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Family Law', '<div itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Review-aggregate">\r\n    <span itemprop="itemreviewed">Banner Jones Family Law Reviews</span>    \r\n    <span itemprop="rating" itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Rating">\r\n      <span itemprop="average">4.5</span>\r\n      out of <span itemprop="best">5</span>\r\n    </span>\r\n    based on <span itemprop="votes">32</span> ratings.    \r\n</div>'),
(221, 'Employment Law', 'employment_disputes', 'Employment Law Solicitors | Chesterfield | Banner Jones ', 80, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2>We are Employment Law specialists in Chesterfield, providing first rate advice on Employment Law From redundancy to discrimination</h2>\r\n<p>Employment Law changes more rapidly than any other area of law. At Banner Jones, we are continuously keeping up to date with the changes in UK employment law. If you believe you have an issue regarding your employment situation, it is best to seek advice as soon as possible due to the nature of the quickly changing employment legislations. At Banner Jones, being employment law specialists means we are on hand to put your mind at ease, and to make sure that your rights as an employee are upheld.</p>\r\n<p>Think you know employment law? We''ve created an employment law quiz to help you test your knowledge on the law around unfair dismissal. See if you can guess whether each case resulted in a successful ruling of unfair dismissal!</p>\r\n<p><a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Employment Law Quiz'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/124_EmploymentLawInfographic.pdf?1434624666" target="_blank"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/221/contained_images/a8130ebfba2a_441_banner-jones-employment-quiz.JPG?1434624508" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="250" /></a></p>\r\n<p class="standout_link" style="text-align: center;"><a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Employment Law Quiz'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/124_EmploymentLawInfographic.pdf?1434624666" target="_blank">Open Quiz</a></p>\r\n<p>If you have an employment problem, often it is something else for consideration within your case, so it is always worth contacting an employment law solicitor and finding out for certain.</p>\r\n<p>At Banner Jones we can advise you on your legal rights regarding employment law, where they relate to the following:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Unfair Dismissal and Disciplinary Proceedings</li>\r\n<li>Maternity and Paternity Rights</li>\r\n<li>Discrimination</li>\r\n<li>Redundancy</li>\r\n<li>Applications to employment tribunals </li>\r\n<li>Any other employment disputes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Expert Employment Law Solicitors</h3>\r\n<p>Our expert employment law solicitors are highly experienced and will treat each case uniquely depending on your circumstances. Our employment law specialists achieve solutions through confidential settlements and are always on hand to provide support when resolving employment law problems. We have worked on many employment law cases and each individual receives the upmost care and consideration throughout the case.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For more information regarding any employment issues, or to arrange an appointment with our expert Employment Law solicitors in Chesterfield, call <span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span>*,&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:employment@bannerjones.co.uk">employment@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>', '2010-11-15 11:04:16', '2015-06-18 11:02:48', 'Expert Employment Law Solicitors in Chesterfield. Contact us now for advice on discrimination, paternity/maternity rights, unfair dismissal or redundancy!', '', 5, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'EmploymentDisputes.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 51721, '2010-12-22 09:44:02', 'Employment Disputes', '', '', 'Employment Disputes', '', '', 4, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '<p><a onclick="_gaq.push([''_trackEvent'', ''Guides'', ''Download'', ''Employment Assist'']);" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/59_Employment - Banner Jones Employment Assist Leaflet  - Updated 07.04.14.pdf?1396882513" target="_blank">Download Banner Jones Employment Assist PDF</a></p>\r\n<p><img src="../../../assets/stored_images/original/237_employment assist.jpg?1389800538" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></p>', 'Employment Law', '<div itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Review-aggregate">\r\n    <span itemprop="itemreviewed">Banner Jones Employment Law Reviews</span>    \r\n    <span itemprop="rating" itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Rating">\r\n      <span itemprop="average">5</span>\r\n      out of <span itemprop="best">5</span>\r\n    </span>\r\n    based on <span itemprop="votes">32</span> ratings.    \r\n</div>\r\n'),
(222, 'Driving Offences', 'motoring_defence', 'Traffic Offences | Driving Offence Solicitors in Sheffield | Banner Jones ', 184, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h1><strong style="font-family: Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">Please note: From 5pm on Friday 24th April 2015 the Banner Jones Solicitors Criminal Defence department became part of&nbsp;<a href="http://www.vhsfletchers.co.uk" target="_blank">VHS Fletchers Solicitors</a>.<br /><br /></strong><strong style="font-family: Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">As a result, if you have a live Criminal Defence matter this has been automatically been transferred.</strong></h1>\r\n<p><strong><span><br /></span></strong><span style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold;">Banner Jones are expert Driving Offence Solicitors</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Speeding In Sheffield</h2>\r\n<p>Do you live in Sheffield? Speeding is a common occurrence. Did you know Sheffield makes almost &pound;300,00 a year from speeding fines? Take a look at the infographic below to find out facts and figures about speeding in Sheffield.</p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/115_Speeding.pdf?1420627418" target="_blank"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/222/contained_images/1e459d4c514d_390_speeding snippet.JPG?1420627491" border="0" alt="Speeding in Sheffield Statistics" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="250" /></a></p>\r\n<p class="standout_link" style="text-align: center;"><a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Speeding in Sheffield'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/115_Speeding.pdf?1420627418" target="_blank">Open Infographic</a></p>\r\n<p>At Banner Jones Solicitors our specialist solicitors assist people accused of driving offences on a regular basis, whether it is at our local courts in Chesterfield, Mansfield, Derby, Nottingham, and Sheffield, or further afield.</p>\r\n<p>With ever advancing technology constantly monitoring our driving more and more, people are finding themselves charged with a road traffic offence and penalties. Whether it&rsquo;s a speeding offence, or a driving offence, they all attract penalties which can quite often lead to significant fines, the endorsement of points on driving licences and ultimately the loss of a licence. Therefore many people require a driving offence solicitor.</p>\r\n<p>For some people, being charged with a traffic offence can lead to them losing their licence, which may then result in them losing their job and other disastrous consequences. Our specialist driving offence solicitors in Sheffield and Chesterfield are experienced in defending or mitigating driving offence charges and penalties, often with the result that a driving ban is avoided.</p>\r\n<p>We deal with a full range of driving offences, with some of the most common ones listed below. We recognise that the reality for most motorists is that they want to know what the court is likely to do to them, and how they can protect their driving licence.</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold;">Driving Offences Advice</span></p>\r\n<p>Our specialist driving offence solicitors can provide advice and guidance in all traffic offences including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/speeding-offences-" target="_blank">Speeding offences</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/drink-and-drug-driving-offences-" target="_blank">Drink driving offences</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/drink-and-drug-driving-offences-" target="_blank">Driving under the influence of drugs</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/careless-driving-" target="_blank">Failing to comply with traffic signals</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/road-traffic-offences-" target="_blank">Defective vehicles</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/road-traffic-offences-" target="_blank">Driving without insurance</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/road-traffic-offences-" target="_blank">Driving whilst disqualified</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/mobile-phone-driving-offences-" target="_blank">Mobile phone driving</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/careless-driving-" target="_blank">Failing to provide information/stop after an accident</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/totting-up" target="_blank">Totting Up Driving Bans</a>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Contact our expert Driving Offence Solicitors</h2>\r\n<p>If you need fast, reliable and professional advice on how to defend a traffic offence charge, and perhaps avoid conviction or disqualification, please contact one of our driving offence solicitors. There are instances where challenges can be made, but it is crucial that you take legal advice before any other action.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment with our expert driving offence solicitors,&nbsp;<strong><strong>call&nbsp;<strong><a href="tel: +441246283000">01246 283000</a></strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:chesterfield@vhsfletchers.co.uk">chesterfield@vhsfletchers.co.uk</a>.</strong></strong></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><strong><strong><br /></strong></strong></strong></p>', '2013-05-01 15:43:43', '2015-07-22 09:07:30', 'At Banner Jones we offer expert advice on traffic offences, we have driving offence solicitors who are able to provide guidance in motoring matters.', '', 5, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0, 'We could help to save your licence!', '107_iStock_000013404152XSmall.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 42987, '2013-05-01 15:47:20', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/101_Driving Offences - Speeding Offences Infographic.pdf?1409053156" target="_blank">Download Speeding Infographic</a></p>\r\n