(223, 'Residential Property', 'residential_property', 'Conveyancing Solicitors in Sheffield | Banner Jones ', 42, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2>At Banner Jones we are expert Conveyancing Solicitors&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p>Selling your home and buying a new one can be one of the most stressful times in your life, what with choosing an estate agent, instructing a conveyancing solicitor and getting your house ready for viewings.</p>\r\n<p>At Banner Jones we are specialist conveyancing solicitors in Sheffield and Chesterfield; we want to take away some of the pressure - our simplified and refined conveyancing process will do just that. We know from experience that the things you care about when instructing a conveyancer are the cost, the speed of the transaction and the conveyancing solicitors assistance and advice.</p>\r\n<p>We have put together a guide on Buying &amp; Selling houses to provide you with some fundamental insight as well as outlining the overall process of each:</p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/62_Residential Conveyancing - Buying and Selling Houses - Updated 07.04.14.pdf?1396883544" target="_blank"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/223/contained_images/9259c4a974cb_349_Conveyancing.JPG?1409049444" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></a></p>\r\n<p class="standout_link" style="text-align: center;"><a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Buying and Selling Guide'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/62_Residential Conveyancing - Buying and Selling Houses - Updated 07.04.14.pdf?1396883544" target="_blank">Open Buying &amp; Selling Houses Guide</a></p>\r\n<h2>Banner Jones Conveyancing Solicitor Specialists</h2>\r\n<p>So why choose Banner Jones as your conveyancing solicitors?</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Members of the Law and Society Conveyancing Quality Scheme since 2012</li>\r\n<li>We are local conveyancing solicitor experts in Sheffield and Chesterfield</li>\r\n<li>We offer competitive and clear conveyancing charges. So you only pay for what you actually need</li>\r\n<li>We regularly check our prices so you don&rsquo;t have to</li>\r\n<li>Reduced transaction times as we use the latest case management systems</li>\r\n<li>The ability to check your conveyancing case online 24/7</li>\r\n<li>Text messages sent to you when key milestones are met.</li>\r\n<li>We give you more. Get our purchase plus package for FREE!</li>\r\n<li>Your transaction will be undertaken by a specialist conveyancing solicitors</li>\r\n<li>The peace of mind of knowing that all work undertaken by us is covered by professional indemnity insurance</li>\r\n<li>We are able to carry out conveyancing transactions anywhere in England and Wales. You will not be required to attend our offices in person</li>\r\n<li>We cover all types of conveyancing transactions</li>\r\n<li>If your conveyancing transaction falls through we will only charge you for the work that has been done</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Conveyancing Services</h2>\r\n<p>At Banner Jones our highly trained experts offer support and care to all of our clients. We also offer a sensitive approach to each case whilst also ensuring that all of our services are fully confidential. We will provide you with informative house conveyancing advice that will help you through the conveyancing process.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment with our expert Conveyancing solicitors, call <span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span></strong>*<strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@bannerjones.co.uk">info@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>', '2010-11-15 10:31:55', '2015-07-22 09:20:55', 'At Banner Jones we are expert conveyancing solicitors. We give advice and can help simplify the conveyancing process. ', 