(224, 'Totting Up', 'totting_up', 'Totting Up Driving Ban | Specialist Driving Solicitors in Sheffield | Banner Jones ', 210, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h1><strong style="font-family: Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">Please note: From 5pm on Friday 24th April 2015 the Banner Jones Solicitors Criminal Defence department became part of&nbsp;<a href="http://www.vhsfletchers.co.uk" target="_blank">VHS Fletchers Solicitors</a>.<br /><br /></strong><strong style="font-family: Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">As a result, if you have a live Criminal Defence matter this has been automatically been transferred.</strong></h1>\r\n<p><strong><span><br /></span></strong><span style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold;">At Banner Jones we offer expert care and advice on the Totting Up Driving Ban Process</span></p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Totting Up Guide</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">To help you avoid totting up points on your licence and to provide you with additional, need to know information, we have developed a Totting Up Guide.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Totting up Guide'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/75_Driving Offences - Totting up guide.pdf?1402501202" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/100_Driving Offences - Totting up guide.pdf?1409045004" target="_blank"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/224/contained_images/22099cc19ffe_302_Totting Up.JPG?1402501396" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></a></strong></p>\r\n<p class="standout_link" style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/100_Driving Offences - Totting up guide.pdf?1409045004" target="_blank">Open Guide</a></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">If you accumulate 12 or more penalty points on your driving licence the court will disqualify you from driving. This is often called "totting up" or being a "totter upper". This is relatively easy to do, and can be the result of a few minor speeding offences over a three year period. This is often the only time that a person appears in court and can be stressful due to the day in court itself, and because of the driving disqualification. It has also been suggested that if you do receive a totting up driving ban your insurance premiums could increase drastically.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">The rules that normally apply say that a driver who accumulates 12 or more penalty points within 3 years will receive a 6 month driving ban as a totter upper. Some courts do exercise discretion and there have been examples of 3 month bans being imposed, however, we would advise you to talk to a qualified driving defence solicitor in Sheffield and Chesterfield who can advise you if it would be possible to convince the court that you should be allowed to keep your licence.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold;">Totting Up Driving Ban Rules</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">If you accumulate 12 points in any 3 years you will face a totting up driving disqualification as your points are valid for 3 years from the date of conviction, but cannot be removed until their fourth anniversary.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Do not be mistaken and assume that you can delay a case to circumvent the totting up rules. If you currently had 9 points on your licence, with 3 points due to expire, delaying the court hearing until after those 3 points have been dropped will NOT mean you will escape disqualification as a totter upper. The court looks at the number of points that were currently on your licence at the time your recent offence was committed.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">The courts, however, do not have to disqualify you. As mentioned, they may allow you to keep your licence if they can be persuaded that in the circumstances it would cause exceptional hardship. Each person and set of circumstances is different, and the court needs to be persuaded to give you another chance. Our specialist solicitors can advise you on this process from your first point of contact, through to appearing at court on your behalf.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Contact our Specialist Driving Offence Solicitors to discuss the Totting Up process</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Our expert motoring offence solicitors are highly experienced in the totting up process, and will treat each case uniquely, as we know each of our clients have different circumstances. Our driving offence specialists achieve solutions through confidential settlements, and are always on hand to provide support, as we understand this can be a stressful and worrying period due to the severe implications. We have worked on many totting up driving ban cases, and we guarantee the upmost care and consideration to all of our clients.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment with our expert driving offence solicitors,&nbsp;<strong><strong><strong>call&nbsp;<strong><a href="tel: +441246283000">01246 283000</a></strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:chesterfield@vhsfletchers.co.uk">chesterfield@vhsfletchers.co.uk</a>.</strong></strong></strong></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><strong><strong><strong><br /></strong></strong></strong></strong></p>', '2014-02-10 13:25:31', '2015-07-22 09:08:22', 'At Banner Jones we offer expert care and advice on a totting up driving ban. Our qualified motoring defence solicitors can advise you of the full process. ', '', 1, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/100_Driving Offences - Totting up guide.pdf?1409045004" target="_blank">Download Totting Up Guide</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/75_Driving Offences - Totting up guide.pdf?1402501202" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/100_Driving Offences - Totting up guide.pdf?1409045004" target="_blank"><img src="../../../assets/stored_images/original/303_Totting Up Icon.JPG?1402501442" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></a></p>', 'Totting Up Driving Ban ', '<div itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Review-aggregate">\r\n    <span itemprop="itemreviewed">Banner Jones Driving Offences Reviews</span>    \r\n    <span itemprop="rating" itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Rating">\r\n      <span itemprop="average">4.5</span>\r\n      out of <span itemprop="best">5</span>\r\n    </span>\r\n    based on <span itemprop="votes">6</span> ratings.    \r\n</div>\r\n'),
(226, 'Discrimination', 'discrimination', 'Workplace Discrimination Advice | Chesterfield | Banner Jones ', 115, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2><strong>Our Employment Law Specialists at Banner Jones provide expert advice on discrimination at work.</strong></h2>\r\n<p>At Banner Jones we pride ourselves on providing expert advice on discrimination at work whether it be sex, race, disability, age, orientation and more - we deal with all types of discrimination.</p>\r\n<p>The grounds for workplace discrimination claims increase all the time so we know you need to feel confident that you have someone to turn to for the latest advice when you need it.</p>\r\n<p>At Banner Jones we ensure our expert discrimination law solicitors are continuously up to date with the latest employment law, therefore guaranteeing you receive first class advice.</p>\r\n<p>See our Discrimination Fact Sheet below for essential information on illegal discrimination, exceptions, types of discrimination and how employers should deal with discrimination:</p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/77_Employment Law - Discrimination Fact Sheet for Employers.pdf?1403267797" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/77_Employment Law - Discrimination Fact Sheet for Employers.pdf?1403267797"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/77_Employment Law - Discrimination Fact Sheet for Employers.pdf?1403267797" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/91_Employment Law - Discrimination Fact Sheet for Employers.pdf?1408705425" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/91_Employment Law - Discrimination Fact Sheet for Employers.pdf?1408705425" target="_blank"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/226/contained_images/9444cf84f664_327_Discrimination Face Sheet.jpg?1403273699" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></a></p>\r\n<p class="standout_link" style="text-align: center;"><a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Discrimination Fact Sheet'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/91_Employment Law - Discrimination Fact Sheet for Employers.pdf?1408705425" target="_blank">Open Fact Sheet</a></p>\r\n<h2>Specialists in Workplace Discrimination</h2>\r\n<p>If you are an employee and feel discriminated against, we can assess your situation and provide you with sound advice as to whether you have a claim. Our highly experienced and knowledgeable discrimination solicitors will support you throughout the process in a professional manner. We understand that individuals who come to us are often stressed and anxious by their current situation at work, therefore we provide a confidential service along with a sensitive approach that you can feel comfortable with.</p>\r\n<p>At Banner Jones we can ensure that you comply with the correct statutory grievance procedure so that you do not endanger the outcome of your case through mistakes in the process. Our professional approach, coupled with our highly skilled workplace discrimination solicitors, will provide you with a first class service.</p>\r\n<p>If you are an employer, we can provide helpful advice to ensure that you are not guilty of discrimination. As an employer, you have a responsibility to ensure your employees can work freely without feeling vulnerable to discrimination. We are able to offer expert advice on all types of workplace discrimination so that you can concentrate on running your business. Our solicitors can keep you informed on the latest changes which could help you avoid making a costly mistake.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>For more information regarding any employment issues, or to arrange an appointment with our expert Employment Law solicitors in Chesterfield, call <span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span>*,&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:employment@bannerjones.co.uk">employment@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>', '2011-01-27 14:25:13', '2015-03-19 11:38:47', 'Our Employment Law Solicitors in Chesterfield provide expert advice on discrimination at work on the grounds of sex, race, disability & more. Contact us now.', '', 5, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>Relocating due to work?</p>\r\n<p>We can help</p>', '43_hand and keys.JPG', 'image/jpeg', 53480, '2011-04-14 15:34:46', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'Discrimination.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 43543, '2011-01-27 14:26:37', 'Discrimination', '', '', 'Discrimination', '/page/residential-property', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '/page/residential-property', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/91_Employment Law - Discrimination Fact Sheet for Employers.pdf?1408705425" target="_blank">Download Discrimination Fact Sheet</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/77_Employment Law - Discrimination Fact Sheet for Employers.pdf?1403267797"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/77_Employment Law - Discrimination Fact Sheet for Employers.pdf?1403267797" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/77_Employment Law - Discrimination Fact Sheet for Employers.pdf?1403267797" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/91_Employment Law - Discrimination Fact Sheet for Employers.pdf?1408705425" target="_blank"><img src="../../../assets/stored_images/original/328_Discrimination Face Sheet Icon.jpg?1403273842" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></a></p>', 'Discrimination At Work ', '<div itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Review-aggregate">\r\n    <span itemprop="itemreviewed">Banner Jones Employment Law Reviews</span>    \r\n    <span itemprop="rating" itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.o