(227, 'Maternity and Paternity Rights', 'maternity_and_paternity_rights', 'Maternity and Paternity Rights & Advice | Chesterfield | Banner Jones', 116, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2><strong>At Banner Jones, our Employment Law Solicitors in Chesterfield provide expert advice on Maternity and Paternity Leave Entitlements<br /></strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p>If you are about to add a new member to your family, congratulations. As a new parent, the birth of a child should be a joyous occasion. Unfortunately, it can be extremely stressful due to problems within your workplace. Our Employment Law Solicitors provide expert advice on both maternity and paternity rights to ensure you are informed on all your rights within the workplace.</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Maternity Rights</strong></h2>\r\n<p>At Banner Jones we often see women being discriminated as soon as they announce that they are pregnant. Our highly trained lawyers can advise on the basic <strong>maternity rights</strong> including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The right not to be dismissed due to pregnancy or childbirth </li>\r\n<li>The right to time off for ante-natal care</li>\r\n<li>The right to alternative work or pay during suspension because of maternity</li>\r\n<li>The right to maternity leave </li>\r\n<li>The right to maternity pay </li>\r\n<li>The right to return to work after maternity leave </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>On returning to work after maternity leave, we ensure that the process is as smooth as possible. We provide all clients with expert advice and support on flexible working hours should they require it and have otherwise been turned down by their employer.</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Paternity Rights</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Unfortunately, paternity rights is an area many employees are uneducated about. It is likely that an employer will be more tolerant towards maternity leave as opposed to paternity leave. At Banner Jones our solicitors are continually up to date with the latest on paternity rights and are able to support any fathers who may be experiencing paternity discrimination at work. We can advise on the basic paternity rights including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Statutory paternity pay </li>\r\n<li>Qualifying period of employment</li>\r\n<li>Obligation to give advance notification to employer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span>Read our leaflet summarising the recent changes to&nbsp;</span><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/10_paternity leave from 3 April 2011.doc?1300984411" target="_blank">Paternity rights</a><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;</span><strong style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">Maternity and Paternity Solicitors</strong></p>\r\n<p>If you are experiencing maternity or paternity leave discrimination, our highly trained maternity and paternity solicitors in Chesterfield are on hand to help solve your issues and provide you with supportive advice. We understand the distress that many of our clients are facing and therefore we offer a sensitive approach to all our clients as well as a confidential service.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For more information regarding maternity and paternity rights, or to arrange an appointment with our expert Employment Law solicitors in Chesterfield, call <span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span>*,&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:employment@bannerjones.co.uk">employment@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>', '2011-01-27 14:27:28', '2015-03-19 11:39:04', 'Contact our Employment Solicitors in Chesterfield today for confidential advice and services relating to your maternity or paternity rights at work.', '', 5, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>Who will look after your child in the event of the unthinkable ever happening?</p>\r\n<p>Make sure you have your say, write a Will today</p>', '34_Family Image.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 276475, '2011-02-28 15:04:32', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'MaternityAndPaternityRights.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 43126, '2011-01-27 14:27:54', 'Maternity and Paternity Rights', '', '', 'Maternity and Paternity Rights', '/page/making-a-will', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '/page/making-a-will', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', 'Maternity and Paternity Rights', '<div itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Review-aggregate">\r\n    <span itemprop="itemreviewed">Banner Jones Employment Law Reviews</span>    \r\n    <span itemprop="rating" itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Rating">\r\n      <span itemprop="average">5</span>\r\n      out of <span itemprop="best">5</span>\r\n    </span>\r\n    based on <span itemprop="votes">1</span> ratings.    \r\n</div>\r\n'),
(228, 'Unfair Dismissal', 'unfair_dismissal', 'Unfair Dismissal Advice | Chesterfield | Banner Jones ', 117, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2><strong>Our expert Employment Law Solicitors in Chesterfield offer advice on Unfair Dismissal and the latest Unfair Dismissal laws</strong></h2>\r\n<p>At Banner Jones, we know losing your job can be very stressful and that&rsquo;s why we will take you through the unfair dismissal claims process step by step. We have a team of highly experienced solicitors who are continually keeping up to date with the latest on unfair dismissal law ensuring we provide you with expert up to date advice.</p>\r\n<p>We have developed an Unfair Dismissal Guide for Employers to provide you with essential information on employment rights, capability, conduct, gross misconduct, redundancy, illegality and automatic unfair dismissals. See below for our guide:</p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/79_Employment Law - Unfair dismissal guide for employees.pdf?1403267821" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/93_Employment Law - Unfair dismissal guide for employees.pdf?1408705469" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/93_Employment Law - Unfair dismissal guide for employees.pdf?1408705469" target="_blank"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/228/contained_images/c980cf39dcbc_325_Unfair Dismissal Guide.jpg?1403273161" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></a></p>\r\n<p class="standout_link" style="text-align: center;"><a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Unfair Dismissal Guide'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/93_Employment Law - Unfair dismissal guide for employees.pdf?1408705469" target="_blank">Open Guide</a></p>\r\n<p>Furthermore, we have put together a Disciplinary Action Guide for Employers featuring procedures, problems and grievances. See below for our guide:</p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/76_Employment Law - Disciplinary Action Guide for Employers.pdf?1403267786" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/90_Employment Law - Disciplinary Action Guide for Employers.pdf?1408705410" target="_blank"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/228/contained_images/c0fc90403a66_329_Disciplinary Action Guide.jpg?1403275348" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></a></p>\r\n<p class="standout_link" style="text-align: center;"><a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Disciplinary Action Guide'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/90_Employment Law - Disciplinary Action Guide for Employers.pdf?1408705410" target="_blank">Open Guide</a></p>\r\n<p>If you are contemplating an employment tribunal proceeding due to unfair dismissal, you will benefit from our advice. It is essential to be guided through the correct procedural steps before making an unfair dismissal claim to an employment tribunal. We can guide you through each step of the unfair dismissal case and our solicitors will make sure you understand the process and help you avoid any pitfalls.</p>\r\n<p>We will not only advise you on the merits of an unfair dismissal case, but also on its potential costs and benefits. We will be upfront and tell you if we believe your unfair dismissal case is likely to succeed. This will help you with your decision to take the claim forward.</p>\r\n<h2>Unfair Dismissal Advice</h2>\r\n<p>At Banner Jones we understand that dealing with an unfair dismissal case can be distressing for our clients. That&rsquo;s why we offer expert support and care to all of our clients. We also offer a sensitive approach to each case whilst also ensuring that all of our services are fully confidential. We will provide you with informative unfair dismissal advice that will help you come to a decision which will benefit you.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For advice on unfair dismissal, or support with an unfair dismissal case; arrange an appointment with our expert Employment Law solicitors in Chesterfield by phone on <span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span>*,&nbsp;or by email at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:employment@bannerjones.co.uk">employment@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>', '2011-01-27 14:28:29', '2015-03-19 11:40:50', 'If you want to start an Unfair Dismissal claim, our Employment Solicitors in Chesterfield are here to help with up to date advice and confidential service.', '', 5, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>Relocating due to work?</p>\r\n<p>We can help</p>', '69_iStock_000003465599XSmall.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 245782, '2011-04-14 15:36:16', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'UnfairDismissal.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 48317, '2011-01-27 14:28:50', 'Unfair Dismissal', '', '', 'Unfair Dismissal', '/page/residential-property', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '/page/residential-property', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/93_Employment Law - Unfair dismissal guide for employees.pdf?1408705469" target="_blank">Download Unfair Dismissal Guide</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/79_Employment Law - Unfair dismissal guide for employees.pdf?1403267821" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/93_Employment Law - Unfair dismissal guide for employees.pdf?1408705469" target="_blank"><img src="../../../assets/stored_images/original/326_Unfair Dismissal Icon.jpg?1403273359" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/90_Employment Law - Disciplinary Action Guide for Employers.pdf?1408705410" target="_blank">Download Disciplinary Action Guide</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/76_Employment Law - Disciplinary Action Guide for Employers.pdf?1403267786" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/90_Employment Law - Disciplinary Action Guide for Employers.pdf?1408705410" target="_blank"><img src="../../../assets/stored_images/original/330_Disciplinary Action Guide Icon.jpg?1403275446" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></a></p>', 'Unfair Dismissal Advice ', '<div itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Review-aggregate">\r\n    <span itemprop="itemreviewed">Banner Jones Employment Law Reviews</span>    \r\n    <span itemprop="rating" itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Rating">\r\n      <span itemprop="average">5</span>\r\n      out of <span itemprop="best">5</span>\r\n    </span>\r\n    based on <span itemprop="votes">1</span> ratings.    \r\n</div>\r\n'),
(229, 'Redundancy', 'redundancy', 'Redundancy Rights | Employment Law Solicitors | Banner Jones ', 118, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2>At Banner Jones, our Employment Law Solicitors in Chesterfield offer expert Redundancy rights advice as well as up to date guidance on redundancy laws</h2>\r\n<p>Redundancy is something that we hear far too often at the moment, but it is an unfortunate fact that most people will go through this at least once in their working life. Being fully informed on your redundancy rights is essential if you are facing redundancy by your employer. At Banner Jones we have expert employment solicitors who are continuously ensuring that they are up to date with the latest on redundancy laws; that way we are able to offer expert redundancy rights advice to all clients.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We have put together a redundancy procedure guide for employers to ouline the full process, selecting people for redundancy, common mistakes and vital information you should consider to be able to make informed decisions. See guide below:</p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/78_Employment Law - Redundancy procedure guide.pdf?1403267808" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/92_Employment Law - Redundancy procedure guide.pdf?1408705445" target="_blank"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/229/contained_images/7ab3e28464e5_321_Redundancy Guide.jpg?1403269011" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></a></p>\r\n<p class="standout_link" style="text-align: center;"><a onclick="pageTracker._trackEvent(''Infographic'', ''Open'', ''Redundancy Procedure Guide'');" href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/92_Employment Law - Redundancy procedure guide.pdf?1408705445" target="_blank">Open Guide</a></p>\r\n<p>If you are currently facing redundancy, Banner Jones can help you make sure that your redundancy rights as an employee are being dealt with in the correct manner.</p>\r\n<p>We are here to take you through the redundancy process step by step and can advise you of your redundancy rights, allowing you to make informed decisions. Your redundancy rights include the following:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Your redundancy payment</li>\r\n<li>Time off to look for another job </li>\r\n<li>The selection procedure and whether it was fair</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>If we feel you have a redundancy case against your employer, we will guide you through the tribunal process step by step, ensuring you are fully educated with the latest redundancy advice. We always give open and honest opinions of the likely outcome, therefore ensuring you make informed decisions.</p>\r\n<p><strong style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">Redundancy Rights advice</strong></p>\r\n<p>At Banner Jones, we understand that being made redundant can be a highly stressful ordeal for any individual to go through. Our highly trained experts offer support and care to all of our clients. We also offer a sensitive approach to each case whilst also ensuring that all of our services are fully confidential. We will provide you with informative redundancy rights advice that will help you come to a decision which will benefit you.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For any advice on redundancy rights, or support with the latest on redundancy laws, call our expert Employment Law solicitors in Chesterfield on <span class="calltracks_bannerjonescouk-main">0330 017 6309</span>*,&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:employment@bannerjones.co.uk">employment@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>*<strong><sub>calls cost no more than a local 01 number and are included in your mobile minutes.</sub></strong></p>', '2011-01-27 14:29:15', '2015-03-19 11:39:26', 'If you''ve been made redundant and you want to check your rights or get advice, our Employment Law Solicitors in Chesterfield are here to help. Contact us now.', '', 5, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '<p>Family circumstances changing?&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You should review your Will</p>', '34_Family Image.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 276475, '2011-02-28 15:27:50', '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'Redundancy.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 47025, '2011-01-27 14:29:35', 'Redundancy', '', '', 'Redundancy', '/page/making-a-will', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '/page/making-a-will', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '<div class="image_left"><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/78_Employment Law - Redundancy procedure guide.pdf?1403267808" target="_blank">Download Redundancy for Employers Guide</a></div>\r\n<div><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/78_Employment Law - Redundancy procedure guide.pdf?1403267808" target="_blank"><img src="../../../assets/stored_images/original/322_Redundancy Icon.jpg?1403269094" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></a></div>', 'Redundancy Rights & Advice', '<div itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Review-aggregate">\r\n    <span itemprop="itemreviewed">Banner Jones Employment Law Reviews</span>    \r\n    <span itemprop="rating" itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Rating">\r\n      <span itemprop="average">5</span>\r\n      out of <span itemprop="best">5</span>\r\n    </span>\r\n    based on <span itemprop="votes">1</span> ratings.    \r\n</div>\r\n'),
(230, 'Speeding Offences ', 'speeding_offences_', 'Speeding Offences | Specialist Driving Solicitors in Sheffield | Banner Jones ', 212, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h1><strong style="font-family: Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">Please note: From 5pm on Friday 24th April 2015 the Banner Jones Solicitors Criminal Defence department became part of&nbsp;<a href="http://www.vhsfletchers.co.uk" target="_blank">VHS Fletchers Solicitors</a>.<br /><br /></strong><strong style="font-family: Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">As a result, if you have a live Criminal Defence matter this has been automatically been transferred.</strong></h1>\r\n<p><strong><span><br /></span></strong><span style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold;">At Banner Jones our expert Driving Offence Solicitors offer expert care and advice on Speeding Offences</span></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>With ever-increasing numbers of speed cameras on Britain&rsquo;s roads, speeding is a very common offence. Last year alone there were over 4 million summonses dealt with by the Magistrates Court, and many were successfully defended by specialists in motoring law, such as Banner Jones.</p>\r\n<p>We have developed an infographic outlining key information, facts and statistics surrounding speeding offences and the law:</p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/89_Traffic Offences - Speeding Offences Infographic.pdf?1408704404" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/99_Driving Offences - Speeding Offences Infographic.pdf?1409044988" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/101_Driving Offences - Speeding Offences Infographic.pdf?1409053156"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/101_Driving Offences - Speeding Offences Infographic.pdf?1409053156" target="_blank"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/230/contained_images/cc6e468cbf58_340_Speeding Offences Infographic 2.JPG?1408704484" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></a></p>\r\n<p class="standout_link" style="text-align: center;"><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/101_Driving Offences - Speeding Offences Infographic.pdf?1409053156" target="_blank">Open Infographic</a></p>\r\n<p>Furthermore, we have produced an article delving deeper in to the speeding offences process, penalties and enforcement:</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/71_Driving Offences - Speeding Offences Advice Guide.pdf?1402497181" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/98_Driving Offences - Speeding Offences Advice Guide.pdf?1409044976" target="_blank"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/230/contained_images/04660ba4cc8d_341_Speeding Article.JPG?1408704529" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></a></p>\r\n<div class="standout_link" style="text-align: center;"><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/98_Driving Offences - Speeding Offences Advice Guide.pdf?1409044976" target="_blank">Open Article</a></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>It can be easy to mistake the speed limit on the roads, or not realise that you are just over the limit.</p>\r\n<p>Driving over the speed limit is something most people would admit to having done at some point in their driving lives. Speeding offences are often dealt with by the police by using Fixed Penalty Notices, and never get to court. The driver admits to speeding and is given penalty points, and pays a fine. Magistrates Courts generally deal with speeding cases because the driver:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Denies the offence</li>\r\n<li>Admits the offence but was travelling at a very high speed</li>\r\n<li>Already has penalty points on their driving licence already and are at risk of disqualification.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Speeding Offences Penalties</h2>\r\n<p>Our specialist solicitors in Sheffield and further afield are well versed in the defences available for speeding offences, and are ready to advise on the specifics of your case. Whether this is a lack of proper speed limit signs, a concern about the speed measuring equipment or simply a case of denying being the driver.</p>\r\n<p>Our solicitors are also well versed in explaining to the court the detailed circumstances of each case and persuading the court to reduce punishment for speeding. If the driver admits the speeding offence, this will result in them having 12 or more penalty points on their driving licence. This is called being a &lsquo;totter upper&rsquo;. Please see our &lsquo;<a href="../../../page/totting-up" target="_blank">totter upper</a>&rsquo; section for more information.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Below is the likely punishment a court will order for the offence of speeding:</strong></p>\r\n<table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="162" valign="top">\r\n<p>Speed Limit (mph)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td colspan="3" width="370" valign="top">\r\n<p>Recorder Speed</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="162" valign="top">\r\n<p>20</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>21-30</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>31-40</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>41-50</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="162" valign="top">\r\n<p>30</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>31-40</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>41-50</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>51-60</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="162" valign="top">\r\n<p>40</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>41-55</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>56-65</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>66-75</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="162" valign="top">\r\n<p>50</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>51-65</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>66-75</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>76-85</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="162" valign="top">\r\n<p>60</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>61-80</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>81-90</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>91-100</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="162" valign="top">\r\n<p>70</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>791-90</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>91-100</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>101-110</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="162" valign="top">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>FINE</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>FINE</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>FINE</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="162" valign="top">\r\n<p>Points/Disqualification</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>3 points</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>4-6 points OR</p>\r\n<p>Disqualify 7-28 days</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="123" valign="top">\r\n<p>Disqualify 7-56 days OR 6 points</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>However, often there are defences available based upon certain &ldquo;special reasons&rdquo;, or proving &ldquo;exceptional hardship&rdquo;. Any type of defence chosen against driving offences requires a specialist solicitor who has handled numerous cases, and has the experience needed to help make your defence likely to succeed.</p>\r\n<p>The penalties for speeding can result in fines, penalty points, speed awareness courses and disqualification, which can all have a significant impacts both stress related and financially.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold;">Find out more information on Speeding Offences</span></p>\r\n<p>If you need expert and reliable advice on how to defend a speeding offence charge, and perhaps avoid conviction or disqualification, please contact one of our driving offence solicitors in Sheffield and Chesterfield. We understand this can be a stressful time for our clients, and therefore we treat each case with the upmost care and consideration. There are instances where challenges can be made, but we encourage you to take legal advice before any other action.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For more information, or to arrange an appointment with our expert driving offence solicitors,&nbsp;<strong><strong><strong>call&nbsp;<strong><a href="tel: +441246283000">01246 283000</a></strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:chesterfield@vhsfletchers.co.uk">chesterfield@vhsfletchers.co.uk</a>.</strong></strong></strong></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><strong><strong><strong><br /></strong></strong></strong></strong></p>\r\n</div>', '2014-02-10 14:40:13', '2015-07-22 09:09:16', 'At Banner Jones our expert solicitors offer care and advice on speeding offences. We provide helpful advice on speeding offence penalties. ', '', 5, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/101_Driving Offences - Speeding Offences Infographic.pdf?1409053156" target="_blank">Download Speeding Infographic</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/70_Traffic Offences - Speeding Offences Infographic.pdf?1402486195" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/89_Traffic Offences - Speeding Offences Infographic.pdf?1408704404" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/99_Driving Offences - Speeding Offences Infographic.pdf?1409044988" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/101_Driving Offences - Speeding Offences Infographic.pdf?1409053156" target="_blank"><img src="../../../assets/stored_images/original/291_Speeding Offences Icon.JPG?1402497035" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/98_Driving Offences - Speeding Offences Advice Guide.pdf?1409044976" target="_blank">Download Speeding Article</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/71_Driving Offences - Speeding Offences Advice Guide.pdf?1402497181" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/98_Driving Offences - Speeding Offences Advice Guide.pdf?1409044976" target="_blank"><img src="../../../assets/stored_images/original/292_Speeding Article Icon.JPG?1402497257" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></a></p>', 'Speeding Offences ', '<div itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Review-aggregate">\r\n    <span itemprop="itemreviewed">Banner Jones Driving Offences Reviews</span>    \r\n    <span itemprop="rating" itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Rating">\r\n      <span itemprop="average">4.5</span>\r\n      out of <span itemprop="best">5</span>\r\n    </span>\r\n    based on <span itemprop="votes">6</span> ratings.    \r\n</div>\r\n');
