(299, 'Loss of Life', 'loss_of_life', 'Loss of Life | Serious Injury Solicitors in Sheffield & Chesterfield', 249, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p><strong>Loss of Life</strong></p>\r\n<p>Thousands of people are killed every year in road accidents, accidents at work or as a result of not receiving due care from medical professionals. If somebody you love has suffered a fatal injury, either as a result of a serious accident or even medical negligence, you may be looking to claim compensation on behalf of them.</p>\r\n<p>At Banner Jones, we understand that losing a family member can have life-altering consequences for those involved. Though no amount of compensation could ever make up for such a tragedy, often family members are left without any financial support after the loss of a partner and any children that may require financial support after the loss of a parent. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Our experienced serious injury solicitors have worked with several clients under these circumstances and have full empathy for your situation. We handle all cases with the care and sensitivity they deserve and we&rsquo;ll be there to guide you through the claims process every step of the way.</p>\r\n<p>Our case study below details a specific case of loss of life compensation that our specialist serious injury solicitors have dealt with.</p>\r\n<p>[case study]</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Second Opinion</strong></p>\r\n<p>Did you know that if you&rsquo;re not happy with the way your case is being handled by your current solicitor, you can change at no cost to you?&nbsp;&nbsp; Serious injury claims need to be dealt with by Solicitors who really understand the complexity of the injuries and can therefore really help you maximise your compensation. If you&rsquo;re not sure how to go about changing solicitor, just ask and we&rsquo;ll talk you through it.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Banner Jones?</strong></p>\r\n<p>Banner Jones is highly experienced in handling claims from serious accidents. Some notable examples include the Hatfield Rail Crash, the Manchester Air Crash and Zeebrugge Ferry Disaster. In such serious cases, getting an experienced serious injury solicitor on your side is critical to help you maximise the amount of compensation you deserve which will help you to secure your future.</p>\r\n<p>Banner Jones has been ranked as Leading Firm in the UK Legal 500 for the last 2 years for their work in Persona Injury Claims.&nbsp; Here is what the Legal 500 say:</p>\r\n<p><em>Banner Jones Solicitors is &lsquo;a very well-organised'' niche PI firm, which handles claims of any size and type. Simon Wright is &lsquo;very astute''; Robert Banner &lsquo;exudes calm and experience'' </em></p>\r\n<p>With our &lsquo;No win no fee&rsquo; approach and our track record of winning 95% of compensation claims, you can feel confident that you&rsquo;ve got nothing to lose with Banner Jones.</p>\r\n<p>Our team of serious injury solicitors are also happy to provide home/hospital visits if you are unable to make it to our dedicated Accident Claims Centre in Chesterfield. Let Banner Jones help you today. Call us today for a free no obligation chat about your situation or simply drop us an email at <a href="mailto:claims@bannerjones.co.uk">claims@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</p>', '2015-07-29 14:26:21', '2015-08-18 13:54:06', 'If you have lost a relative or a loved one as a result of an accident, our serious injury solicitors are here to help you fight for the justice you deserve. Read more.', '', 1, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'Loss of Life.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 45559, '2015-08-18 13:54:06', 'loss of life', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', 'Loss of Life', ''),
(300, 'Amputation and Loss of Limb', 'amputation_and_loss_of_limb', 'Amputation and Loss of Limb | Serious Injury Solicitors', 250, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p><strong>Amputations and Loss of Limb</strong></p>\r\n<p>The loss of a limb can cause severe changes to your quality of life, both physically and mentally. Whatever the cause may be, losing a limb is a serious injury that will take time to come to terms with. The readjustment process following the amputation will be very difficult, not only for the amputee, but for everyone who is close to them too.</p>\r\n<p>Amputation or limb loss can have a devastating effect on someone not only physically, but psychologically and financially too. It is possible that someone going through this experience will need to adapt their homes with new aids and equipment, pay for necessary medical care and manage the psychological side effects of the amputation.</p>\r\n<p>If you or a relative has lost a limb for reasons that weren&rsquo;t your fault, then you will be able to make a claim for compensation. Here at Banner Jones, we understand what a terrible time you are going through and how much an amputation can affect your life. We recognise that supporting someone through this adjustment in their lives is very important.</p>\r\n<p>Our case study below details a specific case of limb loss dealt with by our serious injury department.</p>\r\n<p>[case study]</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Second Opinion</strong></p>\r\n<p>Did you know that if you&rsquo;re not happy with the way your case is being handled by your current solicitor, you can change at no cost to you?&nbsp;&nbsp; Serious injury claims need to be dealt with by Solicitors who really understand the complexity of the injuries and can therefore really help you maximise your compensation. If you&rsquo;re not sure how to go about changing solicitor, just ask and we&rsquo;ll talk you through it.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Banner Jones?</strong></p>\r\n<p>Banner Jones is highly experienced in handling claims from serious accidents. Some notable examples include the Hatfield Rail Crash, the Manchester Air Crash and Zeebrugge Ferry Disaster. In such serious cases, getting an experienced serious injury solicitor on your side is critical to help you maximise the amount of compensation you deserve which will help you to secure your future.</p>\r\n<p>Banner Jones has been ranked as Leading Firm in the UK Legal 500 for the last 2 years for their work in Persona Injury Claims.&nbsp; Here is what the Legal 500 say:</p>\r\n<p><em>Banner Jones Solicitors is &lsquo;a very well-organised'' niche PI firm, which handles claims of any size and type. Simon Wright is &lsquo;very astute''; Robert Banner &lsquo;exudes calm and experience'' </em></p>\r\n<p>With our &lsquo;No win no fee&rsquo; approach and our track record of winning 95% of compensation claims, you can feel confident that you&rsquo;ve got nothing to lose with Banner Jones.</p>\r\n<p>Our team of serious injury solicitors are also happy to provide home/hospital visits if you are unable to make it to our dedicated Accident Claims Centre in Chesterfield. Let Banner Jones help you today. Call us today for a free no obligation chat about your situation or simply drop us an email at <a href="mailto:claims@bannerjones.co.uk">claims@bannerjones.co.uk</a>.</p>', '2015-07-29 14:28:56', '2015-08-18 13:54:34', 'Have you lost or limb or had an amputation as a result of an accident? Our serious injury solicitors are here to help you fight for the justice you deserve. Read more.', '', 1, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'family_highlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'Amputation.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 50209, '2015-08-18 13:54:33', 'amputation', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 'family_highlight', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 0, '', 'Amputation and Loss of Limb', '');
