(50, 'Kate Hyland', 'Solicitor, Mediator', 'KateHyland@bannerjones.co.uk', '01246 209773', 'Marsden Street', '2011-07-27 11:27:39', '2015-03-16 12:32:42', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 36, 'kate H prof.JPG', 'image/pjpeg', 95159, '2011-11-21 15:57:54', 'Kate Hyland Solicitor and Mediator', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'B.Sc (Management and Law), Dublin Institute of Technology', '2009', 'Kate qualified as a solicitor in Ireland, prior to moving to Sheffield in mid 2009. Kate specialises in advising and assisting clients regarding all issues arising from the breakdown of relationships including divorce, co-habitation disputes, financial disputes as well as issues concerning children and domestic abuse. Kate also trained as a mediator in 2011.  \r\n\r\nPrior to working as a solicitor, Kate had a full and varied career as a Marketing and Public Relations Manager in Dublin as well as five years in the USA as Public Relations Associate with the San Francisco Opera. \r\n', '', 'Kate is a member of the Family Mediators Association', 'Assistant Stage Manager at the Abbey Theatre in Dublin ', 'Playing with my son but if I had time, walking, reading, eating out, theatre, films', 'Glass of white wine or a Mojito', 'Exploring the weird and wonderful in the Southern states of the USA', '', 'family mediators.JPG', 'image/pjpeg', 37405, '2012-02-02 12:05:36', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', 'Services for you and your family', '', '', ''),
