(86, 'Laura Barlow', 'Trainee Solicitor', 'LauraBarlow@bannerjones.co.uk', '01246 560508', 'Glumangate', '2014-05-22 14:05:10', '2015-06-22 15:37:24', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 49, 'Laura 3.jpg', 'image/pjpeg', 147264, '2014-05-22 14:05:09', 'Laura Barlow Paralegal business legal services', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'University of Lincoln and Nottingham Law School', 'LLB(Hons) 2012- LPC 2014 ', 'Laura recently started a training contract and is part of the Business Legal Services Department.\r\nLaura has experience in Family Law.', '', '', 'Customer Service Assistant at the Co-op', 'Holidays, Socialising, Musical Theatre', 'Vodka, Lime and Lemonade- suitable for all occasions ! ', 'New York for the shops and Broadway', 'Completing the LPC!!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', 'Services for you and your family', '', '', ''),
(90, 'Debbie Barker', ' Costs Draftsperson', 'DebbieBarker@bannerjones.co.uk', '01246 283 029', 'Marsden Street', '2014-09-05 10:43:08', '2014-10-15 10:02:36', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 38, 'Debbie Barker.jpg', 'image/pjpeg', 233272, '2014-10-15 10:00:32', 'Debbie Barker', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', 'Debbie is an experienced Law Costs Draftsperson who specialises in drafting Clinical Negligence and Public Law legally aided claims as well as claims in Family, Care and Criminal cases.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', 'Services for you and your family', '', '', ''),
(91, 'Katie Ash ', 'Solicitor, Director, Head of Employment Law', 'KatieAsh@bannerjones.co.uk', '01246 560560', 'Glumangate', '2014-10-15 09:39:16', '2015-01-23 10:58:43', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 10, 'Katie Ash.jpg', 'image/pjpeg', 161607, '2014-10-15 09:39:14', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'Sheffield Hallam University and the College of Law', '2004', 'Katie is a Solicitor specialising in Employment Law. She deals with all aspects of employment law and advises a wide range of individuals and private, public and third sector clients with regards to employment law, HR and TUPE issues.\r\n', '', '', 'Paper round followed by pot washing and shop work', 'Family time! Season ticket at Sheffield United and watching junior league football (my nephew), skiing, keeping fit ', 'Anything alcoholic except gin! Probably Prosecco if I had to choose.', 'Disneyland, Florida with my little girl and husband.', ' Being made Head of Employment Law at Banner Jones', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '<span>Katie advises on all aspects of contentious and non-contentious employment law, including claims for unfair dismissal, wrongful dismissal and discrimination. She also advises and supports clients in relation to employment contracts, grievances, disciplinary matters, other policies and procedures and settlement agreements.</span><br /><br /><span>Katie''s particular expertise is in TUPE, the law relating to handling redundancies, collective consultation and trade unions.</span><br /><br /><span>She also has experience in representing clients before the Employment Tribunal, the Employment Appeal Tribunal, the Court of Appeal and in mediation, which includes judicial mediation.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span>Katie acts for both employers and individuals, which enables her to provide straightforward advice and support, having seen the arguments first hand from both sides.</span><br /><br /><span>Katie prides herself on getting to know her clients and building lasting relationships so that clients feel that she is there to support them in finding pragmatic and workable solutions to issues that arise in the workplace.</span>', '', 'Services for you and your family', '', '', ''),
(92, 'Ian Osborn', 'Solicitor', 'IanOsborn@bannerjones.co.uk', '01246 560571', 'Glumangate', '2014-10-15 09:48:11', '2015-03-09 16:54:07', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 18, 'Ian Osborn.jpg', 'image/pjpeg', 153044, '2014-10-15 09:48:09', 'Ian Osborn commercial law', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'MSc in Business with Legal Management Masters and LL.B (Hons) Exempting degree at Northumbria University', '1st August 2014', 'Ian studied both the Solicitors’ Exempting Degree and Business with Legal Management Masters at Northumbria University, prior to completing his training with an entrepreneurial city law firm in Newcastle upon Tyne.  Ian specialises in commercial property and has represented a breadth of commercial landlords and tenants on multifaceted leasehold matters, including assignments, lease surrenders, lettings and sub-leases.  Ian also has experience of advising developers on large property transactions, financial institutions in high-value secured lending or refinancing and corporate organisations in land purchase and disposal.  Ian is able to act for individual clients on purchases and dispositions of residential property, both freehold and leasehold for occupation or buy-to-let.  He has also been instructed by large companies to act in breach of contract litigation relating to land purchase sale agreements and claims for adverse possession, boundary adjustment and property-related dispute resolution.', '', 'Ian sits as the Secretary and Treasurer to the Over Haddon Community Project, a community initiative designed to facilitate and promote a wide sense of community involvement amongst the residents of Over Haddon, their family, friends and beyond through the arrangement, hosting and organisation of local events and meetings.', 'Barman and waiter at the Lathkil Hotel, Over Haddon', 'Medieval history, reading novels, rugby union, running', 'Châteauneuf-du-Pape (or San Pellegrino sparkling water during the working day!)', 'A relaxing two weeks snorkelling and sailing in the Maldive Islands', 'Qualifying as a commercial property solicitor', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', 'Services for you and your family', '', '', ''),
(96, 'Amy Fowlston', 'Paralegal', 'AmyFowlston@bannerjones.co.uk', '01142 703789', 'Sheffield', '2015-03-13 15:54:06', '2015-07-14 11:57:39', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 54, 'DSC_8978Amy Fowlston.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 180285, '2015-03-13 15:54:04', 'AmyFowlstonParalegal', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', 'Since 2010 Amy has worked as a Paralegal, and specialises in the preparation and drafting of Wills.', '', '', 'My first job was an office assistant.', 'My hobbies are going to the gym, running, and spending time with family and friends', 'Kir Royale cocktail', 'Backpacking through Europe', 'Getting the job I am in now!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', 'Services for you and your family', '', '', ''),
(97, 'Kate Skelton', 'Solicitor', 'KateSkelton@bannerjones.co.uk', '01246 560560', 'Glumangate', '2015-03-13 16:32:01', '2015-04-22 14:38:17', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 19, 'DSC_8995 Kate Skelton.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 179766, '2015-03-13 16:31:59', 'KateSkeltonSolicitor', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'Nottingham Trent University', 'April 2010', 'Sales & Purchases including freeholds, leasehold, flats, plots, new builds etc.  Transfer of Equity, Remortgages, Equity Releases and Estate Assents.', '', '', 'Very First- Waitress in a Thai restaurant.\r\nFirst Legal – Paralegal in a property department.', 'Gym, Yoga, spending time with my little boy.', 'Mojito or a good cup of tea.', 'Disneyland Florida.', 'Getting this new Job!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', 'Services for you and your family', '', '', ''),
(98, 'Lee Foster', 'Solicitor', 'LeeFoster@bannerjones.co.uk', '01246 560560', 'Glumangate', '2015-03-13 16:50:34', '2015-03-30 15:34:17', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 39, 'DSC_9003 Lee Foster.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 140088, '2015-03-13 16:50:32', 'LeeFosterSolicitor', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'University of Sheffield and Sheffield Hallam University ', '2002', 'Civil and Commercial Litigation.', 'Successfully defending a Multi-Track Misrepresentation/Fraud claim that ran to trial.', 'Accredited member of Law Society Personal Injury Panel', 'Saturday job in a butchers shop, which mainly involved picking up chicken guts, severed heads and entrails from the floor.', 'Most sports but in particular golf, football, squash and weight training.', 'Gin and tonic or Peroni', 'A villa overlooking 7 Mile Beach, Grand Cayman', 'Stopping my 2 children (aged 3 and 5) from causing each other permanent physical harm on a daily basis.', '135_personal Injury.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 48189, '2015-03-13 16:50:34', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '<p>After qualifying in 2002, Lee continued to developed considerable talents in the areas of Dispute Resolution and Personal Injury Law as he practised throught the Derbyshire county.</p>\r\n<p>Lee represents clients in a wide variety of matters including the following areas:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Commercial Litigation</li>\r\n<li>Contract disputes</li>\r\n<li>Professional negligence</li>\r\n<li>Boundary disputes</li>\r\n<li>Inheritance Act claims/contested probate</li>\r\n<li>Defending fraud/misrepresentation allegations</li>\r\n<li>Debt recovery</li>\r\n<li>Personal Injury Litigation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>A diligently earned wealth of experience provides Lee with a unique insight, which proves to be a significant advantage to clients who instruct him.</p>', '<p>Acted in landmark professional negligence case of Cottingham v Attey Bower &amp; Jones (2000).</p>', 'Services for you and your family', '', '', ''),
(99, 'Kelly Walters', 'Solicitor', 'KellyWalters@bannerjones.co.uk', '01142 703770', 'Sheffield', '2015-03-16 11:01:11', '2015-04-13 10:33:48', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 24, 'Kelly.png', 'image/png', 709732, '2015-03-16 11:01:08', 'KellyWaltersSolicitor', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'BSc (Hons) University of Glamorgan ', '2005', 'Kelly''s experience practising Family Law in a wide range of fields has evolved into particular specialisms in the areas of divorce, civil partnerships, relationship breakdowns, children, finances and domestic violence.', '', 'Resolution First for Family Law', 'Working in a local corner shop.', 'Kickboxing, walking my dogs and stalking Gary Barlow on Twitter.', 'Milk.', 'Any location with my daughter, family and friends.', 'I haven’t got one yet - I will come back to you on this!', '1_ResolutionSpecialist.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 17384, '2015-04-13 10:33:48', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', 'Services for you and your family', '', '', ''),
