(1, 'The service I received couldn''t have been better! ', 'Mrs C, Chesterfield ', '2010-11-18 13:28:05', '2011-09-30 12:45:18', 1, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(2, 'It just goes for me to say thank you for your help and assistance and especially the advice in this matter and should A2Z have the need for similar services.  We will certainly consider Banner Jones first				\r\n', 'A2Z computers, London ', '2010-12-09 10:25:16', '2011-02-10 16:34:07', 1, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(3, 'If in future I need legal advice my preference will be with Banner Jones after such great service', 'Mr Kingston', '2010-12-09 10:25:54', '2011-02-10 16:34:50', 1, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(4, 'Thank you again for your help..If anyone requires a solicitor at any time..I will recommend yourselves..for quick and friendly service				\r\n', 'Miss N, Chesterfield', '2010-12-09 10:26:10', '2011-02-10 16:35:32', 1, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(5, 'Thank You so much for your help and support through this difficult time, the collaborative process worked well for us				\r\n', 'Mrs W, Sheffield', '2011-01-25 10:34:33', '2011-02-10 16:36:06', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(6, 'The service I received was excellent.', 'Mrs B, Dronfield', '2011-02-10 16:36:37', '2011-02-10 16:36:37', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(7, 'I received excellent service for the purchase of my house', 'Mrs S,Sheffield', '2011-02-10 16:37:42', '2011-03-01 12:42:59', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(8, 'Mr Barlow was a gentleman on both visits to my home and I would recommend him.\r\n', 'Mrs B, Chesterfield', '2011-02-28 14:00:25', '2011-02-28 14:00:25', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(10, 'The receptionist staff on both days we visited your office were extremely friendly and the whole experience of dealing with Banner Jones was wonderful', 'T Howard', '2011-02-28 14:02:12', '2011-02-28 14:02:12', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(11, 'Although you are now part of Banner Jones, to me you are still Glossops, and the service we receive is part of why we have been with you for so many years.', 'Mr T Pass', '2011-04-20 15:39:51', '2013-10-28 10:53:57', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(12, 'All is oustanding! \r\n', 'Miss C Chesterfield', '2011-04-20 15:40:44', '2011-09-30 11:57:39', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(13, 'Thankyou Helena Downing for all your excellent service.  You are a credit to the firm. Kind Regards', 'Mr & Mrs W, Alfreton', '2011-07-19 08:37:57', '2015-03-09 15:56:25', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(14, 'Thank you for everything that you have done to help us move house very quickly & smoothly', 'Miss R & Mr D', '2011-07-19 08:38:42', '2011-09-30 11:52:35', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(15, 'I just wanted to say thank you so very much for all the help I was given when I needed advice very quickly. Richard Barlow (Chesterfield ) and Catherine (Dronfield) were so kind, understanding and helpful. My first impresssions of Banner Jones are outstanding and I will not hesitate to contact you in the near future when I will require further assistance. Normally I may feel a little intimidated speaking to a solicitor but was made to feel really at ease.', 'Mrs A, Chesterfield', '2011-07-19 08:39:22', '2013-10-28 10:55:03', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(16, 'I was involved in an accident and my insurance company thought they had achieved the world for me by getting an offer of 50/50. This offer would mean not only would I get 50% of the damage done to my car, but would also lose my no claims bonus. I went to Banner Jones with all the paperwork and just a few weeks later I was banking a cheque for the full amount of damages and had my no claims discount. Great Service!', 'Mr B, Chesterfield', '2011-09-30 11:48:07', '2014-12-18 15:37:19', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(17, 'I would like to put on record my great appreciation of the efficient manner in which you have dealt with the estate.  At all times you have been so helpful and your advice when things seemed to be falling apart has minimised my stress level.', 'Mr S, Sheffield', '2011-11-23 11:17:11', '2011-11-23 11:17:11', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(18, 'I am very grateful for all your efforts and a very satisfactory result.  I cannot thank you enough for a first class service and I will happily recommend you to my friends and family.', 'Mr W, Nottingham', '2012-04-10 10:52:56', '2013-10-28 11:02:19', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(19, 'I would like to put on record my great appreciation of the efficient manor in which you have dealt with the estate.  At all times you have been so helpful and your advice when things seemed to be falling apart has minimised my stress level.  I have ensured that members of the family, with whom I have contact, know the value of your contribution to settling my Aunt''s financial affairs.  It has been a great pleasure working with you and I shall keep in touch when necessary.\r\n', 'Mr S, Sheffield', '2012-05-01 12:26:18', '2013-03-12 15:43:32', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(20, 'Rachel Barlow has just completed the legal arrangements in respect of my divorce.  The service I received was exemplary and I wanted to write to you to let you know this.  I have been pretty constrained in relation to availability to meet and most of our business has been done over email which I appreciated.  Responses have been very timely, updates provided regularly, deadlines hit and fees reasonable.  I contrast this with the service provided by a large law firm in Sheffield in the early part of the year and your approach and that of your staff to customer services, in my view, sets your firm apart.  Your firm, and Rachel in particular, came to me through personal recommendation by a friend and I shall be happy to do the same.  Thank you again.\r\n', 'Mr C, Sheffield', '2012-05-01 12:31:43', '2015-03-09 16:03:24', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(21, 'Thanks for your assistance with my case, your advice has been invaluable, and I would certainly recommend Banner Jones to my family and friends.\r\n', 'Mr P Sheffield', '2012-05-01 12:32:34', '2013-10-28 10:51:08', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(22, 'Thank you very much for your kind assistance and will certainly use your service in the future.\r\n', 'Mr L Derbyshire', '2012-05-01 12:33:23', '2012-05-01 12:33:23', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(23, 'We would like to thank our solicitor acting for us Richard, he did  a great job and was very easy to speak to and very friendly.  Extremely professional and we would use him again in the future.\r\n', 'Mr & Mrs S, Sheffield', '2012-05-01 12:34:17', '2015-03-09 16:14:20', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(25, 'I would like to take the opportunity of thanking you for your services and i can now start to move on with my life.\r\n', 'Mr F, Chesterfield', '2012-05-01 12:37:00', '2012-05-01 12:37:00', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(26, 'The advice Kevin gave me was good, he was easy to contact, I am a very happy client', 'Miss Z, Nottingham', '2012-07-10 10:22:25', '2012-07-10 10:22:25', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(27, 'I have been using the Banner Jones Costs drafting team to prepare my legal aid bills, for over a year.  I find their service to be extremely prompt, accurate and cost effective.  They are always happy to answer my queries, and discuss issues that arise.\r\n\r\nOne big advantage is that, as solicitors themselves, they understand the problems that high street firms face in dealing with public funding issues and are able to offer straightforward practical advice.\r\n\r\nI have been very impressed with the work they have done for me and would recommend them very highly.\r\n\r\n', 'Mr P Jones Dean Thomas & Co Worksop', '2012-08-07 11:19:03', '2012-08-07 11:19:03', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(28, 'I’m very lucky that you were available to complete my divorce case.  When I was in a panic over matters you were so calm, and you very professionally and expertly smoothed out all the bumps that came my way.  ', 'Mrs F, Sheffield', '2013-03-06 13:11:49', '2013-03-06 13:11:49', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 0),
(29, 'Rachel’s highly professional approach and reasonable charges were a great bonus. I valued her detailed, honest advice and guidance and prompt responses throughout', '', '2013-03-25 16:04:12', '2013-03-25 16:04:12', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(30, 'Being available out of hours was invaluable to me at the most critical time when deadlines were looming', '', '2013-03-25 16:04:26', '2013-03-25 16:04:26', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(31, 'The personal touch coupled with her experience and sensible approach made all the difference when dealing with something so complicated and upsetting.  I had almost given up hope of retaining my ability to practise', '', '2013-03-25 16:04:38', '2013-03-25 16:04:38', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(32, 'It was a pleasure having Rachel on my side and I could not have got through it without the expert help and guidance.\r\nI could not fault the service I received and we were ready well in advance!\r\n', '', '2013-03-25 16:05:18', '2013-10-28 10:57:42', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(33, 'Sarah Nadin at Banner Jones Private Clients Department provided excellent advice when setting up my fathers will and enabled me to arrange suitable care home arrangements for my mother with a minimum of worry at a stressful time. Banner Jones helped make a difficult situation much easier to handle.\r\n', 'Mr Turner, Sheffield', '2013-04-10 13:05:35', '2013-04-10 13:05:35', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(34, 'I started to engage Helena Downing in June 2012 on a difficult matter of divorce with jurisdiction and grounds for divorce in dispute. The initial arrangement was that she provide advice on how to conduct and express my initial defence in the English Courts. The advice then given proved very helpful and has led to the achievement of a closed consent agreement between the parties. Banner Jones are now instructed to finalise divorce matters through the English Courts.\r\n\r\nThe service I received has been outstanding in terms of the professionalism of advice given and timelines of actions. I am struck by the huge experience of the Senior Partner and was left in no doubt that my case was fully understood and dealt with effectively, sensitively, and creatively. That the partner is an accredited Consensual Family Lawyer has also proved valuable.\r\n\r\nI consider the service to have been good value for money. The advice given was clearly intended to save me legal costs and has actually saved me money.\r\n\r\nI have no experience of other law firms in the area. Helena Downing at Banner Jones was especially recommended to me, and I am very glad I took that advice.\r\n', 'Dr L, Chesterfield', '2013-04-17 11:24:25', '2015-03-09 15:54:22', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(35, 'The service I received was excellent I wouldn''t hesitate in using your services again and would definitely recommend.', 'Mrs H, Sheffield', '2013-04-17 11:38:59', '2013-04-17 11:42:00', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(36, 'Could not have had a better service. Many Thanks', 'Mr H, Sheffield', '2013-04-23 11:40:08', '2013-04-23 11:40:08', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(37, 'A huge thank you to Melissa Casterton at the Marsden Street office for all her hardwork put into my case.  She was superb throughout.', 'Mr H, Chesterfield', '2013-04-23 11:49:39', '2013-04-23 11:49:39', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(38, 'Graysons with Watsom Esam Solicitors have been utilising the cost drafting service of Banner Jones for the last 6 months particularly for our Family Law and Legally Aided matters.  We have been highly satisfied with the service provided. We would particularly commend upon the speed of return, the accuracy of the billing and the assistance given to ourselves and the Fee Earners specificallywhere issues have arisen. This has allowed us to improve our own efficiency and profitability', 'Kate Fitzpatrick, Graysons with Watsom Esam', '2013-04-26 11:48:23', '2013-05-23 09:27:48', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(39, 'Thank you very much for all your help, support and a great outcome of my case.', 'Mr W, Chesterfield', '2013-05-02 13:57:17', '2013-05-02 13:57:17', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(40, 'Very happy with the service, Richard Joy has been excellent.', 'Mr L, Sheffield', '2013-05-02 14:02:49', '2013-05-02 14:02:49', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(41, 'We are very satisfied with Bannr Jones.  May I also say the Receptionists and Secretaries were kind, helpful and courteous.', 'Mr & Mrs W, Chesterfield', '2013-05-02 14:18:02', '2013-10-28 10:58:54', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(42, 'I thought my Solicitor and his secretary were excellent.  Thanks', 'Mr D, Chesterfield', '2013-05-14 12:50:31', '2013-05-14 12:50:31', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(43, 'A year ago we sold our house, and the work was handled by Marissa Layton of Banner Jones. \r\n\r\nProblems arose which were the result of actions, or lack of action, by others, and these difficulties were compounded when they continued over a time when we were out of the country. \r\n\r\nMarissa Layton worked wonders on our behalf, keeping us informed at every stage of the proceedings despite the distances involved. \r\n\r\nThe sale eventually completed successfully. I was so impressed by the way the sale was handled that I have no hesitation in recommending Banner Jones and Marissa Layton unreservedly. If I ever need advice in the Chesterfield area again I shall happily return to Banner Jones. \r\n', 'Mr W, Milton Keynes ', '2013-05-15 12:56:04', '2013-05-15 12:56:04', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(44, 'I found Ruth to be very professional and caring throughout my case at Crown Court.  Ruth was always at hand to answer my queries, she always put me at ease during my most stressful situations even coming to my home to take statements when I wasn''t fit to travel. Ruth treated me as a friend and made me feel comfortable and at ease.\r\n\r\nI will always be very grateful to Ruth for the time and effort she gave me.  If I ever need legal representation again then Ruth would be the first person I would contact.\r\n', 'Mr B, Chesterfield', '2013-05-21 10:28:54', '2013-05-21 10:28:54', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(45, 'Chesterfield Law Centre regularly use the legal costing services of Banner Jones for our Housing certificated work and are extremely pleased with the level of service we receive, "the work is consistently of a high and accurate standard, our bills are then processed by the LAA without reduction. We would highly recommend the service."  ', 'Lisa Haythorne, Chesterfield Law Centre', '2013-05-23 09:04:32', '2013-05-23 09:21:24', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(46, 'Having recently used the costs service at Banner Jones I was very impressed with the work done. The work was done speedily and well within the time limits I was working to. I was impressed with the documents prepared and the advice given. Stephen Haythorne Solicitor - Sheffield City Council', 'Stephen Haythorne Solicitor - Sheffield City Council', '2013-05-23 09:14:44', '2013-05-23 09:14:44', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(47, 'Richard has completed four purchase and sale transactions for our Company this year. All have been completed efficiently and effectively and to the agreed timescales. We have always found Richard approachable, easy to contact and astute in all matters of contractual detail. We intend to continue to use his services for future property transactions and thank him for all he has done for us over the last twelve months.', 'White Peak Enterprises Ltd.', '2013-06-05 09:26:04', '2013-06-05 09:26:04', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(48, 'Karen, you are indeed a credit to your employers and your profession and I will not hesitate to contact you again should the need arise.', 'Mr S, Dronfield', '2013-07-23 09:42:35', '2013-07-23 09:42:35', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(49, 'I want to thank Annette Thomas for her help and hope she continues to help people like she did me, all the best for the future.', 'Mr S, Newbold', '2013-07-23 12:35:05', '2013-07-23 12:35:05', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(50, 'Thank you  for being so helpful and understanding in the making of our Wills, you gave us good advice and everything was done in a professional manner.', 'Mr C, Chesterfield', '2013-08-13 10:57:31', '2013-08-13 10:57:31', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(51, 'Excellent service received', 'Mr P, Mansfield', '2013-08-13 11:10:31', '2013-08-13 11:10:31', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(52, 'My move to London went very smoothly with thanks to Banner Jones, I wish you had an office here.', 'Mrs P, London', '2013-08-13 11:38:03', '2013-08-13 11:38:03', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(53, 'very supportive service, at each stage I was informed and felt confident with the service.', 'Mr B, Matlock', '2013-08-14 12:28:52', '2013-08-14 12:28:52', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(54, 'We are very satisfied with Banner Jones.  May I also say the receptionists and secretaries were very kind and helpful.', 'Mr & Mrs W, Chesterfield', '2013-08-14 12:59:11', '2013-08-14 12:59:11', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(55, 'Lee Bellingham looked after our case, and was just wonderful. He provided sensitive professional support by phone, email and in person when required, and we are very grateful for everything he did. We would have absolutely no hesitation in recommending him and the services at Banner Jones Solicitors. Lee''s emails were particularly helpful, they were always clear and to the point,  but he treated us with empathy and was excellent at communicating at all levels. Thank you Lee!', 'Mr L, Dronfield', '2013-08-21 11:01:16', '2013-08-21 11:01:16', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(56, 'Professional yet personal & understanding.  Excellent service', 'Mr P, Chesterfield', '2013-08-27 12:51:01', '2014-01-23 17:16:38', 2, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(57, 'I can not fault Mr Banner in any way for the work he did for me.  He was friendly and professional and he managed the case to my benefit.  Thank you.', '', '2013-09-03 11:50:53', '2013-09-03 11:50:53', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(58, 'I would like to take this opportunity to thank you for all you have done for me. I am really pleased with the outcome and I will always be grateful.\r\nI will definatley be recommending Banner Jones to Family, Friends, Colleagues etc should they ever need legal advice and if in the future I myself need legal advice I will definitely return to Banner Jones for this.  Once again thank-you so much for all your hard work.\r\n', 'Ms C, Sheffield', '2013-11-06 14:17:36', '2013-11-06 14:17:36', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(59, 'The speed and professionalism throughout were excellent. They''ve got their finger on the button', 'Mr Nash', '2013-11-06 14:21:08', '2013-11-06 14:21:08', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(60, 'I am very happy with the way that my case was handled and I am positive that this will be my one and only time in prison.', 'Mr H, Chesterfield', '2013-11-06 14:24:37', '2013-11-06 14:24:37', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(61, 'Karen was excellent for our many house purchases / sales - very kind with my elderly parents.', 'Anonymous', '2013-11-06 14:28:22', '2013-11-06 14:28:22', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(62, 'I don''t see how you can improve your service. I had two appointments and each time I was served quickly and excellently.  Just like the days Mr Marks, we have been customers since the 1950''s ', 'Mrs R, Chesterfield', '2013-11-06 14:31:52', '2013-11-06 14:31:52', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(63, 'I just wanted to say Thank You for the work that banner jones have done for me over the last few months.  Marissa has just completed registering the Deeds to the house in my name. Everyone I have dealt with from obtaining letters of administration to the registration of the Deeds have been efficient  and so easy to deal with. Your two receptionists dealt me in a very kind and professional manner. You seem to have excellent staff and I had no hesitation in recommending you to other people.', 'Mrs. B, Chesterfield', '2013-11-06 14:36:47', '2013-11-06 14:36:47', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(65, 'I would recommend Banner Jones for all types of legal work. I was looking for anything up to five years in prison for possessing a knife in a public area and thanks to the legal skill of Banner Jones and specifically Annette Thomas I got four months at the crown Court in Derby.  Thanks so much', 'Mr S, Chesterfield', '2013-11-18 11:21:34', '2013-11-18 11:21:34', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(66, 'We have used Banner Jones for employment advice for over 20 years and the team have always found the best approach to resolve our problem', 'Mr. Richard Kay, Operations Manager, Stagecoach East Midlands', '2013-11-18 11:26:59', '2014-01-23 17:16:40', 2, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(67, 'Thank you for your help and support during the collaborative process. Your calm, pleasant and helpful  attitude made the process much less traumatic than I was expecting', 'Ms P, Sheffield', '2014-01-13 14:11:55', '2014-01-13 14:11:55', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(68, 'I really don''t know how to thank you for the outstanding professional service that you have provided to us in this matter, and I would wish to include Annette in this compliment. If the situation ever arises I would not hesitate in employing your firm, and certainly I am now an advocate for Banner Jones.', 'Mr V, Chesterfield', '2014-01-13 14:14:15', '2014-01-13 14:14:15', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(69, 'I write to express my thanks and satisfaction for the way Mr. Maxwell handled the sale of our property. It was at all times friendly and very professional. He dealt with everything expeditiously and we are grateful for his involvement.', 'Mr M, Mansfield', '2014-01-13 14:16:20', '2015-03-09 16:48:50', 2, 2, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(70, 'I would like to thank Natalia Shaw for her excellent support and advice during our house sale and purchase. She has kept us well informed and has made time to keep us up to date. It has been much appreciated and she has been a pleasure to deal with. ', 'Mrs G, Chesterfield', '2014-01-13 14:17:27', '2014-01-13 14:17:27', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(71, 'On behalf of John & myself, I''d like to thank you very much for the efficient service you gave in dealing with the estate of our aunt.  Thank you too, for your patience and advice when dealing with our many questions.', 'Mrs A, Chesterfield', '2014-01-13 14:19:08', '2014-01-13 14:19:08', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(72, 'Mr Sowter was very likeable, friendly and helpful and I feel he represented me very well indeed', 'Mr. S, Chesterfield', '2014-01-17 16:23:24', '2014-01-17 16:23:24', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(73, 'Excellent quality of work.  Thank You for your time and work.', 'Mr. G, Chesterfield', '2014-01-17 16:25:06', '2014-01-17 16:25:06', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(74, '“Bob,  Just a quick letter to say thanks for always being there, I know you do your best for me and I do recommend you to all.  And a Thank You to the man from Bilton Hammond who came to Mansfield to help me with my case, he was a diamond like you Bob”', 'Mr. J, Chesterfield', '2014-01-17 16:27:31', '2014-01-17 16:27:31', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(75, 'Thank you so much for all your hard work.  I appreciate it’s your job, but to a layperson like myself the assistance of skilled professionals in such matters is invaluable and excellent service makes the minefield of property transfers - which can be so stressful - so much easier.\r\n', 'Mrs. V, Sheffield', '2014-01-17 16:31:03', '2014-01-17 16:31:03', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(76, 'Excellent Service', 'Mr P, Chesterfield', '2014-01-22 14:29:05', '2014-01-22 14:29:05', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(77, 'Both Jade and Sally were efficient, committed, positive and enthusiastic. I felt they were on my side.', 'Mr. H, Dronfield', '2014-01-22 14:33:40', '2014-01-22 14:33:40', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(78, 'If all the firms'' solicitors are as professional, friendly, competent and efficient as Karen Askew you will always have a full work load', 'Mrs. G, Bridlington', '2014-01-22 14:37:30', '2014-01-22 14:37:30', 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
